\c 1
\s1 Isarhe Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima
\r (Umat 3.1-12; Irh 3.1-9,15-17; Uyoh 1.19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Itirhi Isarhe Iyiki Ize iyi Uyesu Ukiristo, Ungw…õŐÉ Unum.
\p 
\v 2 Umb…Ē aka ats…õng ru ubvur uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uishaya ri itsinga ag…õ,
\q1 <<Umum iwuri idene ungw…õŐÉ itsermum agbaashia ru ungo.
\q2 Unga awuri igbishuwa atsń©ndń©ngo.\f + \fr 1.2 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Umrh 3.1\xt*\ft .\f*
\q1 
\v 3 Urh…õm uw…Ē…Ē uyisa ra arhum ug…õ,
\q1 <Agbishuwe utsń©ndń© Uteijee,
\q2 aka agbisha avii atsń©ndń©nga arhika.> >>\f + \fr 1.3 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uish 40.3\xt*\ft .\f*
\m 
\v 4 Nggee Uyohana aba, asorhuwe ub…Ētisima ra arhum na adzowe isarhe iyi idzidzipa iyiki itsŇ©we arhim.
\v 5 Anera arh…õrh…õ abi abń© Uyahudiya, nu aner Urusharhima adzek azń© ru unga. As…Ēm arhimmb…Ē, unga asorhuwe umb…Ē ub…Ētisima ra Az…õŐÉ Urdun.
\p 
\v 6 Uyohana atsim atorho igwar urhakumi, abow ikp…Ēm ubvur n√ļ upfurhsń©nga, ubinghanga uwu asusu nggu utoo arhum.
\v 7 Isarhanga h√£ iy…õ ug…õ, <<Uw…Ē…Ē ruw…Ē aka iba ru undzingmum ag…Ēnga umum, uwuruwi umum isi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉ inggarhukŇ© arhi abadaknga.
\v 8 Umum isorhuwa umbi ub…Ētisima nggu am…õŐÉ, b…Ēr unga awuri ikŇ© Ipfu Isarsatangge asorhuwa.>>
\s1 Ub…Ētisima nu undeya Uyesu
\r (Umat 3.13-17; 4.1-11; Irh 3.21-22; 4.1-13)
\p 
\v 9 Ri ivang h√£ Uyesu adzeka ru Unazarat ra abń© Ugarhirhi, Uyohana asorhuwe unga ub…Ētisima ra Az…õŐÉ Urdun.
\v 10 Uyesu aka awuri idzeka ra am…õŐÉ, unga any√£ af√£ aka ayanga, Ipfu Isarsatangge ru nyaku unurh…õu icipuwa nu unga.
\v 11 Urh…õm udzeka af√£ ug…Ēr ug…õ, <<Ungo uwu Ungw…õŐÉmum iki ń©bema. Nggu ungo umum igŇ©ib…õn akarh√£rh√£.>>
\p 
\v 12 Kanying Ipfu-Num ikŇ©na unga idzek izń©ngge ra arhum.
\v 13 Unga awu um…Ē uts…õku inuma is…Ēka inaa, Ushaitan aka adeya unga. Unga awu nggu √≠ju…õ arhum, b…Ēr √≠pfu itser-Num it…ĒŐÉwe unga itser.
\s1 Uyisa angw…õŐÉ imesa abi inggbaashia
\r (Umat 4.12-22; Irh 4.14-15; 5.11)
\p 
\v 14 Umb…Ē aka agbange Uyohana ru ugborzń© amaa, Uyesu azń© atsń©√£ Ugarhirhi, anu idzowe Isarhe Iyiki Ize iyi Unum.
\v 15 Ag…õ, <<Ivanga iki ibangge! Nggay…õ Iy…õrhu Unum iki iyongge. √Äka adzipa, na awe ru imangmang ri Isarhe Iyiki Ize!>>
\p 
\v 16 Uyesu aka az…õŐÉrh√£ at…Ēng ru ubang Ukau Ugarhirhi, unga any√£ Usiman nu ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē Uandarawu anu itang igber ru ukau ha, umb…Ē awu abika ad…õm ab…õrh.
\v 17 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka aba ad…Ēsa umum, umum itsu umbi awu abika adzui anera.>>
\v 18 Kanying umb…Ē aneke itang igbermb…Ē na ad…Ēsa unga.
\p 
\v 19 Unga aka ag…Ēpa azń© ukunjiir, unga any√£ Uyaku ungw…õŐÉ Uzabadi nu ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē Uyohana ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē, ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ igbishu igbermb…Ē.
\v 20 Asi id√£rhŇ©mb…Ē unga ayisa umb…Ē. Umb…Ē aneke ut…õmb…Ē Uzabadi nggu abi itser imang ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē ha na ad…Ēsa unga.
\s1 Uyesu awayiwe ipfu iyiki ibewe
\r (Irh 4.31-37)
\p 
\v 21 Uyesu nggu angw…õŐÉ imesanga atsń©mb…Ē Ukafanahum, unum ukpuku uwosha uku uwe, Uyesu atsń© ru ub√£ if…õn-Num atirhi imesuwe.
\v 22 Anera adzeidzeu ri imesanga, ubinkutsu amesuwe umb…Ē ru nyaku uner ijee. Asi iwea ru nyaku uwuku umesuwe Ikpem.
\v 23 Um…Ē h√£ uner uw…Ē…Ē ru ub√£ if…õn-Nummb…Ē awuri ipfu iyiki ibewe itsu ivum ig…õ,
\v 24 <<Iyee! Ungo ubee use nggu um…õn Uyesu uner Unazarat? Ungo uba itsń©me um…õn? Umum ihw…õng ungo uwu usarkasar uwu Unum!>>
\p 
\v 25 Uyesu ats…õrhi ipfu iyiki ibewe ha ag…õ, <<Unukutata! Upfudzeka ru utsak ha!>>
\v 26 Ipfu iyiki ibewe ha iyung utsak ha nggu uv…Ēm ni itsu ivum idzengge ru utsak ha.
\p 
\v 27 Anera kishoo adzeidzeu na arhusa ad…Ēka ag…õ, <<Awu use nuwi ik…õi? Imesa iyiki ifa nu ijee! Atsu √≠pfu iyiki ibewe id…Ēsa arherhanga!>>
\v 28 Kanying isarhanga it…õŐÉrh√£ imaangge ananga ra abń© Ugarhirhi.
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe uz…Ēma Ubitru
\r (Umat 8.14-15; Irh 4.38-39)
\p 
\v 29 Umb…Ē aka adzeka ru ub√£ if…õn-Num h√£, umb…Ē azń© nggu Uyaku nu Uyohana atsń©mb…Ē ri iyamb…Ē Ubitru nu Uandarawu.
\v 30 Uya uts…õŐÉ Ubitru iyora imani unga anu inŇ©, umb…Ē as…Ēme unga kanying.
\v 31 Nggee unga azń© adzur uboknga abera unga. Imani iyor ha ikerhungge, unga asok at…ĒŐÉwe umb…Ē itser.
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe anera arh…õrh…õ
\r (Umat 8.16-17; Irh 4.40-41)
\p 
\v 32 Nu urh…õ…õ ha, unuma uku utsń© anera akŇ© arh…õrha abi √≠rh√£rh√£ aba ru Uyesu, nu abi √≠pfu iyiki ibewe.
\v 33 Arh…õrha anera ru utepa ak…Ēng nu angwń© iyaa.
\v 34 Uyesu akerhuwe abi ikpŇ© √≠rh√£rh√£. Ik…õi atsusuwe √≠pfu iyiki ibewe ra anera arh…õrh…õ, asi ibeenga √≠pfu iyiki ibewe irherha arherhe ubinkutsu ngge ihw…õngngge unga.
\s1 Uyesu azń© af…õn-Num ra anangk…õ // anera aka ashimb…Ē
\r (Irh 4.42-44)
\p 
\v 35 Ri ig…ĒŐÉkpeka, uzń© na ub…Ērkp…Ē, Uyesu asok, aneke iya ha na azń©√£ ra anangk…õ anera aka ashimb…Ē, um…Ē unga aka af…õn-Num.
\v 36 Usiman nu abirab…õ aka awu nggu unga azń©mb…Ē ibea unga.
\v 37 Umb…Ē aka any√£ unga, umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Kishoo ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ibea ungo.>>
\p 
\v 38 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Um…õn izń©m…õn iteuy…õ iki ikhapa nggimi, umum idzowe isarhe um…Ē ik…õi. Ubin h√£ ru ukp…Ē uku ukŇ© umum uba.>>
\v 39 Nggee unga az…õŐÉrh√£ amaa Ugarhirhi adzowe isarhe ra ab√£ if…õn-Nummb…Ē na atsusuwe √≠pfu iyiki ibewe ra anera.
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe uner ingbim
\r (Umat 8.1-4; Irh 5.12-16)
\p 
\v 40 Uner ingbim uw…Ē…Ē aba ru Uyesu, atararhu ash…ĒŐÉrh√£ unga ag…õ, <<Ungo uba ubeengo, ungo ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ukerhuwango umum nu usara umum.>>
\p 
\v 41 Um…Ē Uyesu agŇ© atorh, aberu uboknga abangu utsa ha. Ag…õ, <<Umum ń©beemum, ukerhe!>>
\v 42 Kanying ingbimnga ikerhungge.
\p 
\v 43 Uyesu asoyiwe unga na avange atonga akarh√£rh√£ ag…õ,
\v 44 <<Niba us…Ēmuk…Ē unera. B…Ēr uzń©, ud…õyiwe itsingo ru uwuku udzowe id…õm-Num nu udzowe id…õm-Num iyi Umusa aka amesuwa umbi ri ikikerhe, ra anera ahw…õng ug…õ ungo uku ukerhungo.>>
\v 45 Unga aka ikorhe rimi, utsak ha akpurha adzek ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ isis…Ēme anera, amaa ananga kishoo. Ak…õr…õ ha atsu Uyesu asi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ atsń©√£ uteu ukp…Ē…Ē ri inyń©ny√£ anera, akpurha aseiyi ru awiya anangk…õ anera aka ashimb…Ē um…Ē. Rimi h√£ anera anang adzeyi ri inang aba ru unga.
\c 2
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe uner ishai iyor
\r (Umat 9.1-8; Irh 5.17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Inuma ukunjiir iki it…Ēng, Uyesu abvui atsń©√£ Ukafanahum ik…õi, anera aka agŇ© ug…õ unga aka aba ri iya.
\v 2 Anera arh…õrh…õ ak…Ēng at…Ēke ub√£√£, atsu ananga asi ib…Ērke ru angwń© ub√£√£, Uyesu adzowe umb…Ē isarhe.
\v 3 Inera inaa iki its√£ uner irh√£rhń© ishai iyor akŇ© aba.
\v 4 Umb…Ē aka asi ikpomb…Ē udń© ukpuku utsutsń© ru Uyesu, anera aka arh…õmb…Ē, umb…Ē afŇ© ati akang uvi iya ha ra anank…õ Uyesu aka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ, na acipuwe uner ishai iyor ha nu ufarnga aka anu.
\v 5 Uyesu aka any√£ imangmangmb…Ē, unga ag…Ēr uner ishai iyor ha ag…õ, <<Ungw…õŐÉmum, aka atsŇ©w√£mb…Ē arhimngo.>>
\p 
\v 6 Abika amesuwe Ikpem asei um…Ē ra anang h√£ akaif…õrhk…Ē ra am…õnmb…Ē ag…õ,
\v 7 <<Awu use utsu utsak uwur…õ arherhe rimi? Unga aka arhenu Unum! Ungam…Ē awe ru ijee iyiki itsŇ©we arhim? Asi iwea Unum ikiyikanga?>>
\p 
\v 8 Kanying Uyesu ahw…õnga ubinkpi umb…Ē aka akaif…õrhk…Ē ra am…õnmb…Ē, unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu umbi awe ru ikpŇ© if…õrhk…Ē ha?
\v 9 Akasong aka ayoa, umb…Ē aka id…õyiwe uner ishai iyor ha, <Aka atsŇ©w√£mb…Ē arhimngo,> use ig…Ēr ug…õ, <Usisok unyangu ufarngo uz…õŐÉrh√£?>
\v 10 B…Ēr umum ibee umbi ahw…õng ug…õ Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner awea ri ijee iyiki itsŇ©we arhim ru upfung.>> Um…Ē unga ag…Ēr uner ishai iyor ha ag…õ,
\v 11 <<Umum ń©g…Ēr ungo, usisok, unyangu ufarngo uzń© ri iya.>>
\v 12 Unga asok, anyangu ufarnga az…õŐÉrh√£ adzeka ri inyń©ny√£ anera kishoo. Ak…õr…õ ha atsu umb…Ē adzeidzeu na akpoi Unum ag…õ, <<Um…õn inasi iny√£m…õn if…õrh…õ rimi.>> \fig Uyesu ag…Ēr uner ishai iyor ha ug…õ unga asisok|alt="Jesus tells the paralytic to stand and walk" src="dn00444b.tif" size="col" loc="2.12" copy="Darwin Dunham" ref="2.12"\fig*
\s1 Uyisa ukpu Urhawi
\r (Umat 9.9-13; Irh 5.27-32)
\p 
\v 13 Uyesu abvui adzek azń©√£ ru ubang Ukau Ugarhirhi. Anera arh…õrh…õ aka azń© ak…Ēng adziira unga, unga amesuwe umb…Ē.
\v 14 Unga aka az…õŐÉrh√£ at…Ēng, unga any√£ Urhawi ungw…õŐÉ Uharhfa aka asei ra anang akika ay…õi ikirbi abń©. Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ud…Ēsa umum,>> unga asok ad…Ēsa unga.
\p 
\v 15 Uyesu nu angw…õŐÉ imesanga asei igha urh…õ…õ ri iya Urhawi nggu abika ay…õi ikirbi abń© nu abirab…õ aka anyanga umb…Ē awu abi arhim arh…õrh…õ. Anera arh…õrh…õ aka ad…Ēsa unga.
\v 16 Ivangy…õ abika amesuwe Ikpem aka awu abi Ufarisi, aka any√£ unga aka asei igha ubingha nggu abi arhim h√£ nu abika ay…õi ikirbi abń©, umb…Ē arhusa angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu unga asei igha ubingha nggu abika ay…õi ikirbi abń© nu abi arhim?>>
\p 
\v 17 Uyesu aka agŇ© rimi, unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Abika aker asi ibeemb…Ē uner ag…Ēu, abi irh√£rh√£ ukpekŇ© abee uner ag…Ēu. Umum isi ń©bamum iyisa abika arhurhika, b…Ēr umum ń©ba iyisa abi arhim.>>
\s1 Arhusu Uyesu ikpem ighabin
\r (Umat 9.14-17; Irh 5.33-39)
\p 
\v 18 Angw…õŐÉ imesu Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima nu abi Ufarisi ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ikpem ighabin. Anera ab…Ē…Ē aba arhusu Uyesu ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu Angw…õŐÉ imesu Uyohana nu abi Ufarisi akpemmb…Ē ighabin, b…Ēr abingo asi ikpemmb…Ē?>>
\p 
\v 19 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu aw…õrhu utsak uwuku ufa akpem ighabin unga aba ana awu nggu umb…Ē? Asi √≠kpemmb…Ē ri ivangy…õ unga aka awu nggu umb…Ē.
\v 20 Ivanga niy…Ē ibar…Ē umb…Ē awuri isoyiwe utsak uwuku ufa ha ru umb…Ē, unum h√£ nukp…Ē umb…Ē aka ikpem ighabin.
\p 
\v 21 <<Unera asi √≠kŇ© utatorho uku ufa abipunga atorho aka agbe. Unga aba akorhunga, utatorho uwuku ufa ha uwuri ishń©rh√£ avaate atorho aka agbe ha, ivivaar ha iwuri inangge iyi inggbaashia.
\v 22 Ik…õi unera asi √≠tsuka am…õŐÉ inebi aka afa ra amb√£ń© aka agbe. Unga aba akorhunga rimi, am…õŐÉ inebi aka afa ha awuri iyare amb√£ń© aka agbe ha, amb√£ń© ha nu am…õŐÉ inebi ha awuri iwe ib…õm. Am…õŐÉ inebi aka afa, awuri itsu ake ra amb√£ń© aka afa.>>
\s1 Uteijee uwu unum ukpuku uwosha
\r (Umat 12.1-8; Irh 6.1-5)
\p 
\v 23 Ru unum ukpuku uwosha ukp…Ē…Ē, Uyesu nu angw…õŐÉ imesanga az…õŐÉrh√£ at…Ēng ri icang arhkama. Angw…õŐÉ imesanga aka az…õŐÉrh√£ nggu unga, atirhi igbiu atsi arhkama.
\v 24 Abi Ufarisi ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Uny√£, awu use utsu umb…Ē azharhuwe Ikpem unum ukpuku uwosha?>>
\p 
\v 25 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi anasi ivarhumbi ubin Udauda aka akorhe ri ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka agŇ© imerh nggu aw…õrhu uz…õŐÉrh√£nga?
\v 26 Ri inum Uabiata aka awu Ukug…Ēng Uwuku Udzowe Id…õm-Num, Udauda atsń© ri Iya-Num, at√£iwe usarkasar uborodi, ik…õi na ab…Ēr adzowe aw…õrhu uz…õŐÉrh√£nga, ukpurukpi uku usi im…õŐÉkp…Ē unera at√£inga ukp…Ē, uner uwuku udzowe id…õm-Num ukpekŇ© awuri it√£i.>>
\p 
\v 27 M…Ēc…õ unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Angw…õŐÉwe unum ukpuku uwosha ra anera, asi ingw…õŐÉmb…Ē anera awemb…Ē abi unum ukpuku uwosha.
\v 28 Nggee Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner unga awu Uteijee uwu unum ukpuku uwosha.>>
\c 3
\s1 Uner ushai ubok ru Ukafarnahum
\r (Umat 12.9-14; Irh 6.6-11)
\p 
\v 1 Ivang iy…Ē…Ē unga aka atsń© ru ab√£ if…õn-Num, uner uw…Ē…Ē um…Ē nggu uboknga ushushai.
\v 2 Ab…Ē…Ē abee ubinkpi umb…Ē aka ikŇ© akpo uvau ru Uyesu. Umb…Ē atsu asumb…Ē nu unga use unga awuri ikikerhuka utsak ha ru unum ukpuku uwosha.
\v 3 Uyesu ag…Ēr uner uwuku ushai ubok ha ag…õ, <<Udzek ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ra asumb…Ē kishoo.>>
\p 
\v 4 Uyesu arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Im…õŐÉ…õŐÉ umb…Ē akorhu use ru unum ukpuku uwosha, akorhi iyiki ize use akorhi iyiki ibewe, af…Ērhe urh…õ use af…õre umgb…Ē?>> B…Ēr umb…Ē asei ukutata.
\p 
\v 5 Unga arhi adziira umb…Ē ra av…Ēm, am…õnnga adake ra am…õn aka akermb…Ē, unga ag…Ēr uner ushai ubok ha ag…õ, <<Unamu ubokngo.>> Unga anamu uboknga udzek, Kanying ukp…Ē ukerhukp…Ē.
\v 6 M…Ēc…õ abi Ufarisi adzek ak…õki itsŇ©w√£ nggu aner Uhiridu, abee udń© ukpuku uf…õr Uyesu.
\s1 Ikik…Ēng id…Ēsu Uyesu
\p 
\v 7 Uyesu adzek nggu angw…õŐÉ imesanga azń©mb…Ē ubang ukau, arh…õrha anera adzeku Ugarhirhi ad…Ēsa unga.
\v 8 Umb…Ē aka agŇ© abink…õ unga aka akorhe kishoo, anera arh…õrh…õ aka adzeku Uyahudiya aba ru unga, nu Urusharhima, nu Uidumiya, nu abi ugar Az…õŐÉ Urdun, nu aner Utaya nu Usidon.
\v 9 Anera aka arh…õmb…Ē, unga ag…Ēr angw…õŐÉ imesanga akpowe ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ uwuku uci adzowe unga, utsur anera afń©ń©mb…Ē unga.
\v 10 Unga akerhuka anera arh…õrh…õ, nggee abi irh√£rh√£ abee izń© ra asu abanga unga.
\v 11 Ivangy…õ √≠pfu iyiki ibewe iki iny√£ unga, ngge igba n√ļ abń© ra anangnga ni itsui ivum ig…õ, <<Ungo uwu Ungw…õŐÉ Unum!>>
\v 12 B…Ēr unga avange ngge niba id…õyikungge unera unerwi unga aka awe.
\s1 Is…õng abi itser Uyesu us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn
\r (Umat 10.1-4; Irh 6.12-16)
\p 
\v 13 Uyesu afŇ©√£ igŇ© na ayisa abirab…õ unga aka abee, umb…Ē aba ru unga.
\v 14 Unga as…õng us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn umb…Ē aka iwe abi itser Uyesu ug…õ umb…Ē awe nggu unga, n√ļ unga adene umb…Ē adzek adzise isarhe.
\v 15 Umb…Ē awuri iyiy…õimb…Ē ijee iyiki itsusuwe √≠pfu iyiki ibewe.
\v 16 Umb…Ē h√£ ab…õ, us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£ unga aka as…õng, Usiman, uwu ha Uyesu aki iyisa Ubitru,
\v 17 nu Uyaku ungw…õŐÉ Uzabadi nu ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē Uyohana, abirab…õ Uyesu iki iyisa ug…õ Ubuwarnaji, agbena agburh <<Angw…õŐÉ Igbigbashu Inai,>>
\v 18 nu Uandarawu, nu Ufirhibu, nu Ubatorhomi, nu Umatiyu, nu Utoma, nu Uyaku ungw…õŐÉ Uharhfa, nu Utaddiyu, nu Usiman uner Ukan'ana,
\v 19 nu Uyahuda Uiskariyoti uwuku ugha adaknga.
\s1 Uyesu nu Uba'arhzaburh
\r (Umat 12.22-32; Irh 11.14-23; 12.10)
\p 
\v 20 M…Ēc…õ Uyesu abvui atsń© ri iya. Anera abvui ak…Ēng ik…õi, uts…õku unga nu angw…õŐÉ imesanga asi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ aghamb…Ē ubingha.
\v 21 Abi iyamb…Ē aka agŇ© rimi, asok azń©mb…Ē idzur unga. Anera anu ig…Ēr ag…õ, <<Unga aka azh…Ēmu ukpong!>>
\p 
\v 22 Abika amesuwe Ikpem igamb…Ē adzeku Urusharhima aba ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Awu Uba'arhzaburh uy…õrhe √≠pfu iyiki ibewe unga atsń© ru unga! AkŇ© ijeenga ik…õi atsusuwe ipfu iyiki ibewe idzek.>>
\p 
\v 23 Nggee Uyesu ayisa umb…Ē na arherhuwe umb…Ē unyaka arherhe ag…õ, <<Ushaitan awuri ikorha aguse na awayiwe Ushaitan?
\v 24 Iy…õrhe iba igaungge itsingge, iy…õrha ha isi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉngge.
\v 25 Iya iba igauke itsike, iya ha isi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉke.
\v 26 Rimi Ushaitan aba ugapa itsinga, unga asi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉnga, imimashanga iki ibangge.
\v 27 Idzidz…õrhe, unera asi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉ atsń©√£ ri iya uner uwuku uker akarhuka abinnga, awuri itirhi abow uner uwuku uker ha. M…Ēc…õ unga awuri id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ avura abin iya ha.
\v 28 Umum id…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, kishoo arhim nu irhenu Unum anera aki ikorhe, awuri itsitsŇ©wŇ©kumb…Ē ake.
\v 29 B…Ēr ub…õn uwuku urhenu Ipfu Isarsatangge asi √≠tsŇ©wŇ©kumb…Ē unga, awu ra arhim aki ugbagbaa.>>
\p 
\v 30 Unga arherhe rimi, ubinkutsu umb…Ē aka ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Unga awe ru ipfu iyiki ibewe.>>
\s1 Uya Uyesu nu angw…õŐÉmb…Ē
\r (Umat 12.46-50; Irh 8.19-21)
\p 
\v 31 M…Ēc…õ uya Uyesu nggu angw…õŐÉmb…Ē aba atsń©. Ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ n√ļ awiya, na adene uw…Ē…Ē unga ayisuwe Uyesu.
\v 32 Ikik…Ēnga isei adziira unga, umb…Ē ad…õyiwe unga ag…õ, <<Uyango nu anapumbi abeea ungo ra awiya.>>
\p 
\v 33 Unga arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu umb…Ē ungam…Ē awu uyamum nu angw…õŐÉm…õn?>>
\p 
\v 34 Unga arhi abirab…õ aka asei adziira unga na ag…õ, <<uyamum uwi nggu angw…õŐÉm…õn!
\v 35 Ub…õn unera aka ikorhu ubinkpi Unum aka abema, unga awu ungw…õŐÉm…õn nu unapum…õn nu uyamum.>>
\c 4
\s1 Unyaka arherhe uner uwuku // udoi abin
\r (Umat 13.1-23; Irh 8.4-15)
\p 
\v 1 Ik…õi Uyesu atirhi imesuwe n√ļ ubang ukau. Ikik…Ēnga iki ik…Ēng idziir unga irh…õngge, unga asok atsń© ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ asei ru ukau, ikik…Ēng anera id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ um…Ē n√ļ ubang ukau ha.
\v 2 Unga akŇ© unyaka arherhe amesuwe umb…Ē abina arh…õrh…õ, ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ,
\v 3 <<√Äka akpeto! Uner irham adzek azń© idoi ikpŇ©nga.
\v 4 Unga aka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ inna ikpŇ© h√£, ikpŇ© iy…Ē…Ē igba n√ļ utsń©ndń©, anunu aba akp…Ēuke iyi ha.
\v 5 Iy…Ē…Ē igbei ru ukp…Ērha, abń© asi iweke akarh√£rh√£. Ngge im…õr kanying ubinkutsu, abń© anang h√£ asi ighorke.
\v 6 Unum uku urhang, imani ikoikungge ikpŇ© iyi ha, ubinkutsu ngge ishingge ra anŇ©nang.
\v 7 IkpŇ© iy…Ē…Ē igba ri idid…Ēk, idid…Ēk iseng itong iyi ha, ngge isi ighw…õrngge ikpŇ©rh√£.
\v 8 Iy…Ē…Ē ik…õi igba ra abń© aka aze. Im…õr idzeka, iseng ni ighw…õr ikpŇ©rh√£, iy…Ē…Ē is…Ēka itaitaar, iy…Ē…Ē is…Ēka ut…ĒŐÉt…ĒŐÉń©, iy…Ē…Ē ananaka.>>
\p 
\v 9 M…Ēc…õ Uyesu ag…õ, <<Ub…õn unera aka awu ra ato akika agŇ©, neke unga agŇ©.>>
\p 
\v 10 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka asei ikiyikanga, angw…õŐÉ imesanga us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn nu ab…Ē…Ē aka ad…Ēsa unga arhusa agben unyaka arherhe ha.
\v 11 Unga ad…õyiwe umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Aka adzaamb…Ē umbi ihw…õng iwiw…Ēk Iy…õrhe-Num. B…Ēr abirab…õ aka awu ra awiya, abina kishoo awuri irherhuwe umb…Ē ru unyaka arherhe.
\v 12 Ngge itsu,
\q1 << <Umb…Ē awuri irhirhimb…Ē,
\q2 b…Ēr asi √≠ny√£mb…Ē,
\q1 awuri igŇ©mb…Ē ik…õi
\q2 na asi √≠hw…õngmb…Ē,
\q1 utsur umb…Ē adzipa na atsŇ©wŇ©kumb…Ē arhimmb…Ē!> \f + \fr 4.12 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uish 6.9,10\xt*\ft .\f*>>
\p 
\v 13 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi asi ihw…õngmbi agben unyaka arherhe ha? Ude umbi awuri ikorhu uguse na ahw…õng agben unyaka arherhe ak…Ē…Ē?
\v 14 Uner irham h√£ adoi Arherhu-Num.
\v 15 Ab…Ē…Ē awu ru nyaki ikpŇ©y…õ iki igba n√ļ utsń©ndń©, anangk…õ umb…Ē aka adoi arherha ha, kanying Ushaitan aba atsŇ©wŇ©ka arherhe ha aka adoi ru umb…Ē.
\v 16 Abirab…õ aka awu ru nyaki ikpŇ© iyiriy…õ umb…Ē aka adoi n√ļ abń© ifa, agŇ© arherha ha, kanying umb…Ē ay…õi ake nggu it…õnam…õn.
\v 17 B…Ēr umb…Ē aka ashimb…Ē ra anŇ©nang, umb…Ē ad√£rhń© ivanga ukunjiir. Ivang ayetnum use uver iki iba ri itsi arherha ha, kanying umb…Ē abvui azń©mb…Ē ra andzing.
\v 18 Ik…õi ab…Ē…Ē, awu ru nyaki ikpŇ©y…õ iki idoi ri idid…Ēk, agŇ© arherhe ha,
\v 19 b…Ēr igŇ© ighong abin upfung, nu irhirh…õm ibee iwu ru ubin nu ikpona abina ak…Ē…Ē itsń© ik…õnke arherha ha ighwighw…õr.
\v 20 Ab…Ē…Ē, awu ru nyaki ikpŇ©y…õ iki idoi na abń© aka aze, agŇ© arherha ha, na ay…õi ake akŇ© at…ĒŐÉ itser nggu ake, aghw…õr ikpŇ©rh√£ iy…Ē…Ē is…Ēka itaitaar, iy…Ē…Ē is…Ēka ut…ĒŐÉt…ĒŐÉń©, iy…Ē…Ē ananaka.>>
\s1 Irhirhang afaf√£
\r (Irh 8.16-18)
\p 
\v 21 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi aka isaka agaar irhirhang aw…Ēkmbi ru ikikń©ń©? Use atsuke ngge ra ada ukoma? Ishingge rimi, ug…õse umbi aka isaka aden ngge ru anang id…õŐÉ…õŐÉke afaf√£?
\v 22 Abink…õ aka awu ri iw…Ēk, umb…Ē awuri iny√£mb…Ē ake, abink…õ aka awoyi ik…õi, awuri inyiny√£mb…Ē ake nu awiya.
\v 23 Ub…õn unerwi aka awu ra ato akika agŇ©, neke unga agŇ©.>>\fig Irhirhang nu utsur|alt="Lamp on a mortar" src="hk00152b.tif" size="col" loc="4.23" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="4.21"\fig*
\p 
\v 24 Na ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka akpeto na agŇ©. Ugbiu ha ungo uku ukŇ© umei, awuri ikŇ© umgb…Ē amei adzaa ungo, awuri itomuwamb…Ē ungo.
\v 25 Uwuruwi aka awe ru ihwihw…õng awuri itomuwe unga akpo arh…õrh…õ. Uwuruwi aka ashia, awuri iy…õse ungw…õŐÉrhń© ihwihw…õng ha unga aka awerangge.>>
\s1 Unyaka arherhe ikpŇ© iyiki isiseng
\p 
\v 26 Na ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Iy…õrhe Unum iwuri imin…õ. Unera adoi ikpŇ© nu icangnga.
\v 27 Utsuu nu atenum, unga arha na asok, uts…õki ikpŇ© h√£ iki im…õr iseng, uner ha asi ihw…õnga ubinkpi uku ukorhe.
\v 28 Abń© nibikake atsu ikpŇ© im…õr, atirhi akŇ© agam adzeka, na akŇ© azang adzeka, nu azanga akŇ© ishaanga idzeka.
\v 29 Ivang ishaanga iki ik…ĒŐÉ, unga aka ikŇ© ikon agb…õr, ivang iyiki igb…õr iki iwe.>>
\s1 Unyaka arherhe ishaa umustad
\r (Umat 13.31-32,34; Irh 13.18-19)
\p 
\v 30 Uyesu ik…õi ag…õ, <<Umum ikpangu Iy…õrhe Unum nggu use, umum ikŇ© unyaka arherhe akasong id…õyiwe ngge iki iwe?
\v 31 Iwu ru nyaki ishaa ikpŇ© umastad, iyiriy…õ ngge iki iwe iyiki icia ri ikpŇ© abin iyiki idoi nu abń©.
\v 32 Umb…Ē aka idoi ngge, ngge iki isaki iseng ig…Ēngngge abink…õ umb…Ē aka adoi ra abń©, nggu abokngge akag…Ēng anunu aka isaka acipuwa akang ashiake nu ake.>>
\p 
\v 33 Nggu urh…õrh…õ unyaka arherhe Uyesu aka akŇ© as…Ēme anera Arherhu-Num, ri ihwihw…õngmb…Ē.
\v 34 Asi is…Ēmuka umb…Ē ubin rimi ru umb…Ē uku ushikp…Ē ru unyaka arherhe. B…Ēr ivangy…õ unga aka awu nggu angw…õŐÉ imesanga ikiyikamb…Ē, unga aka isaka as…Ēmuka umb…Ē agbena.
\s1 Uyesu ad…Ē…Ēte ugba inai
\r (Umat 8.23-27; Irh 8.22-25)
\p 
\v 35 Ru unum h√£ urh…õ…õ uku uwe, unga ag…Ēr angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<Um…õn inggar udiku ukp…Ēr…Ē.>>
\v 36 Umb…Ē ab…Ēre ikik…Ēng anera, umb…Ē ashupa unga nggu umb…Ē, ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ unga aka asei ru umgb…Ē. Akhukh…Ē…Ē ak…Ē…Ē ik…õi awu um…Ē.
\v 37 Nggaa ugba ukom ukerketakp…Ē usoyi, am…õŐÉ ukau ha ukw…õr ukhukh…Ē…Ēmb…Ē, uts…õku umgb…Ē ub…Ēr ukunjiir ri idid…õ…õ ra am…õŐÉ.
\v 38 Uyesu awu ru urh…Ē ra akpok ukhukh…Ē…Ē nu ubin ukpuku utsorhi itsi. Angw…õŐÉ imesanga azita unga ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<A umarhem, ungo usi igŇ©o ighong um…õn iki iwuri itsń©m…õn?>>
\p 
\v 39 Unga asok, ats…õrhu ugba ukukom h√£ ag…Ēr am…õŐÉ ukau ukug…Ēng h√£ ag…õ, <<Unukutata! Ud…Ē…Ēr!>> M…Ēc…õ ugbaa ukpekp…Ē, ananga kishoo anukutata uku ughw…Ē…Ēw.
\p 
\v 40 Unga ag…Ēr angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu umbi agŇ© iwei rimi? Umbi ana ashimbi ri imangmang?>>
\p 
\v 41 Umb…Ē agŇ© iwei akarh√£rh√£ ag…Ēr ad…Ēkamb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu ungaa nuwi? Ugba ukom nu ubvun am…õŐÉ agŇ©na unga!>>
\c 5
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe uner ipfu iyiki ibewe
\r (Umat 8.28-34; Irh 8.36-39)
\p 
\v 1 Umb…Ē azń© atsń© ugar ukau abń© Ugarasa.
\v 2 Ivang Uyesu aka adzeku ukhukh…Ē…Ē, unga agbang nggu uner ipfu iyiki ibewe aka adzeka ra anang aka adzak aner.
\v 3 Uner ha asei ra anang akika adzak aner, unera asi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ abowpa unga uko nggu iny√£w√£.
\v 4 Umb…Ē aka isaka abow aboknga nu adaknga nggu iny√£w√£, b…Ēr unga aka isaka apupuwe ngge na abvŇ©ń©we az…Ēu aki adaknga. Unera ashia ri iker iyiki ikp…Ēm unga.
\v 5 Nu utsuu na atenum unga agh…õta ra anang akika adzak aner nu √≠gŇ© anu itsuyi √≠vum na akŇ© atarh angw√£i iyornga.
\p 
\v 6 Unga aka any√£ Uyesu ukukaa, unga atń©tser aba atararhu ra anangnga.
\v 7 Atsarhi irhaknga atsu √≠vum ag…õ, <<Awu use utoma ungo nggu umum, Uyesu, Ungw…õŐÉ Unum uwuku Ug…Ēng? Uyirh itsok Unum ug…õ ungo usi √≠dzaango umum uver!>>
\v 8 Ubinkutsu Uyesu aka ag…Ēra unga ag…õ, <<Upfudzeka ru utsak uwur…õ, ungo ipfu iyiki ibewe!>>
\p 
\v 9 Uyesu arhusa unga ag…õ, <<Itsokngo igburh ungam…Ē?>>
\p Unga ag…õ, <<Itsokmum igburh Ukpusha, ubinkutsu um…õn iwu irh…õ…õm…õn.>>
\v 10 Unga ash…ĒŐÉrhŇ© Uyesu akarh√£rh√£ utsur unga awayika umb…Ē adzemb…Ē ra anang h√£.
\p 
\v 11 Arhede arh…õrh…õ aka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ugh√£w√£ akhapa ri igŇ©a.
\v 12 √ćpfu iyiki ibewe ha ish…ĒŐÉrhŇ© Uyesu ig…õ, <<Uma udena um…õn izń© ru arhede ak…Ēr…Ē, itsń© ra ake.>>
\v 13 Nggee unga abemuka √≠pfu iyiki ibewe ha idzek izń©ngge ru ikpui arhede ha. Ikpui arhede ha itsń©ngge anaka ag…Ēnga avaa, ake asok atń©tser, ahwarha acipa atsń©ke ru ukau atsń©mke ra am…õŐÉ.
\p 
\v 14 Abi idz…õu arhede ha atń© azń© as…Ēme uteumb…Ē nu ukpuku ukhapa um…Ē adzise isarhe, anera adzeyi aba iny√£ ubinkpi uku ukorhe.
\v 15 Umb…Ē aka aba atsń© ru Uyesu umb…Ē any√£ utsak ha ukpui √≠pfu iyiki ibewe ha iki iwe ru unga, asei um…Ē atsim atorho ri iyornga am…õnnga awu uku urhirhiki, iwei if…õr umb…Ē.
\v 16 Abirab…õ aka any√£ if…õrha ha iki ikorhe adzowe isarhe abink…õ aka akorhe nggu uner ukpui √≠pfu iyiki ibewe nu ikpui arhede ha.
\v 17 M…Ēc…õ anera atirhi ish…ĒŐÉrhŇ© Uyesu unga ab…Ēre abń©mb…Ē.
\p 
\v 18 Uyesu awuri itsń© ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ nukpi, utsak ha √≠pfu iyiki ibewe ha iki idzeku unga ash…ĒŐÉrhŇ© Uyesu ama aneke unga ad…Ēsa unga.
\v 19 B…Ēr Uyesu asi inekuka unga. Ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Uzń© ri iya ra angw…õŐÉmbi, us…Ēme umb…Ē abin aka ag…Ēngk…õ Uteijee aka akorhuwa ungo, nu atorhk…õ unga aka agŇ© ru ungo.>>
\v 20 Nggee utsak ha, azń© atsń©rh√£ ri iteu us…Ēka umb…Ē iki iyisa Udikaforhi adzise isarhe, abink…õ Uyesu aka akorhuwe unga. Anera kishoo adzeidzeu.
\s1 Unapa Uyayiru nu uts…õrh uwuku // urhong adzirh
\r (Umat 9.18-26; Irh 8.40-56)
\p 
\v 21 Ik…õi ivang Uyesu aka agar ugar ukp…Ēr…Ē ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ, anera arh…õrh…õ ak…Ēng adziir unga nu ubang ukau ha.
\v 22 M…Ēc…õ unying ra anggbaashi ub√£ if…õn-Num itsoka igburh Uyayiru, aba um…Ē. Unga aka any√£ Uyesu, unga agba ra adaknga,
\v 23 ash…ĒŐÉrh√£ unga ag…õ, <<Ungw…õŐÉrhŇ© unapmum akpurha ab…Ēr akpe. Umum ish…ĒŐÉrh√£ ungo uba utsorhu ubokngo nu unga akerhe na ab…õk.>>
\v 24 Nggee Uyesu azń©√£ nggu unga.
\p Anera arh…õrh…õ aka afń©ń© ad…Ēsa unga.
\v 25 Uts…õrh uw…Ē…Ē um…Ē aghong irh√£rh√£ um…õŐÉ…õŐÉ im…õka us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn.
\v 26 Irh√£rh√£nga ighong unga akarh√£rh√£ ri ivangy…õ abi ag…Ēu arh…õrh…õ aka an…õta unga. Af…õre ubinkpi unga aka awerakp…Ē kishoo, b…Ēr asi igŇ©a ugarh, irh√£rh√£ ikpurhi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ititoma.
\v 27 Ivangy…õ unga aka agŇ© isarhe Uyesu, unga ad…Ēsa unga ra andzing ri ikik…Ēnga, aba abanga atorho Uyesu,
\v 28 ubinkutsu unga akaif…õrhk…Ē ra am…õnnga ag…õ, <<Umum ń©ba ń©bangumum atorhanga ukpekŇ©, umum iwuri ikerhumum.>>
\v 29 Kanying um…õŐÉ…õŐÉnga ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉkp…Ē, nu unga agŇ©√£ ri iyornga aka akerhunga ru ayetnumnga.
\p 
\v 30 Kanying Uyesu agŇ© ijee iki idze ru unga. Unga adzipa ri ikik…Ēnga arhusa ag…õ, <<Ungam…Ē abanga atorhamum?>>
\p 
\v 31 Angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ungo uny√£ anera arh…õrh…õ afń©ń©a ungo rimin…õ ungo ug…Ēr ug…õ, <Ungaa abanga umum?> >>
\p 
\v 32 B…Ēr Uyesu arhi adziir abee iny√£ uwuku ukorhu ubin h√£.
\v 33 M…Ēc…õ uts…õrh ha, aka ahw…õng ubinkpi uku ukorhuwe unga, aba nggu iwei nu izang iyor, agba ra anangnga ad…õyiwe unga kishoo idzidz…õrhe.
\v 34 Unga ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A unapmum, imangmango ngge ikerhuwa ungo. Uzń© uku ut…Ē…Ē, ayetnumngo aka amaake.>>
\p 
\v 35 Uyesu ana awu ra arherhe nukpi, nu anera adzeki iya Uyayiru unggbaashi ub√£ if…õn-Num h√£, aba ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Unapungo aka akpea. Awu use utsu ungo unu idzowe umarhem ayetnum?>>
\p 
\v 36 B…Ēr Uyesu akw…õ…õte arherhamb…Ē, ag…Ēr unggbaashi ub√£ if…õn-Num h√£ ag…õ, <<Niba ugŇ©a iwei, uwe ru imangmang ukpekŇ©.>>
\p 
\v 37 Asi ineke unera azń©√£ nggu unga, akpurha akŇ© Ubitru, nu Uyaku, nu Uyohana ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē Uyaku.
\v 38 Ivang umb…Ē aka azń© atsń© ri iya unggbaashi ub√£ if…õn-Num h√£, Uyesu any√£ idzidzunamb…Ē, nu anera aka aciu akpe atsui ivum.
\v 39 Unga atsń© ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu umbi aciu akpe na atsui √≠vum rimi? Una h√£ anasi ikpea awu ru urh…Ē!>>
\v 40 B…Ēr umb…Ē anyń©rh√£ unga.
\p Nggee unga atsu umb…Ē adzek ra awiya, unga akŇ© utesa nu uyisa una h√£ nu angw…õŐÉ imesanga h√£ abika awu nggu unga, atsń© ra anangk…õ una h√£ aka awe.
\v 41 Adzur ubok una h√£ ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Tarhita kumi!>> agbena agburh <<Unakuci, umum ig…Ēr ungo, usisok!>>
\v 42 Kanying una h√£ asok az…õŐÉrh√£ adziir. Im…õknga iwu us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn. Ak…õr…õ ha atsu umb…Ē adzeidzeu akarh√£rh√£.
\v 43 Uyesu agbiite atomb…Ē akarh√£rh√£ ug…õ umb…Ē niba ad…õyikumb…Ē unera. Ik…õi unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē adzowe ubingha ru una h√£.
\c 6
\s1 Akp…õŐÉmb…Ē Uyesu ru Unazarat
\r (Umat 13.53-58; Irh 4.16-30)
\p 
\v 1 Uyesu asoka um…Ē abvui azń©√£ Unazarat utepunga, angw…õŐÉ imesanga azń© nggu unga.
\v 2 Unum ukpuku uwosha uku uwe, unga atirha amesuwe ru ub√£ if…õn-Num, anera arh…õrh…õ aka agŇ© unga, adzeidzeu na arhusa ag…õ, <<Utsak uwur…õ akpo abin ak…õr…õ ri in…õŐÉ…õŐÉ? Adzowe unga itsoi iy…õr…õ ri in…õŐÉ…õŐÉ unga aka anu ikorha abin idzeu?
\v 3 Uw…õr…õ ha asi iwea ukapinta ha, ungw…õŐÉ Umaryamu, ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē Uyaku, nu Uyusuf, nu Uyahuda nu ik…õi Usiman? Asi iwea anapumb…Ē ab…õ nggu um…õn?>> Umb…Ē akp…õŐÉmb…Ē unga.
\p 
\v 4 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num aka isaka akpoa ig…Ēng ru ub…õn ananga, akpurha asheru utepunga nu anernga nu abi iyanga.>>
\v 5 Unga asi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ akorhunga abin idzeu ngg…Ē…Ē ha, unga akpurha atsorhuwe abok nu abi irh√£rh√£ ukunjiir akerhuwe umb…Ē.
\s1 Uyesu adene angw…õŐÉ imesanga
\r (Umat 10.5-15; Irh 9.1-6)
\p 
\v 6 Unga adzeidzeu umb…Ē aka ashimb…Ē ri imangmang.
\p M…Ēc…õ Uyesu atsń©rh√£ adziir √≠teu iyiki ici um…Ē h√£ amesuwe anera.
\v 7 Unga ayisa angw…õŐÉ imesanga us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£ azń© ru unga, unga adene umb…Ē ivaivaa na adzowe umb…Ē ijee ri itsi √≠pfu iyiki ibewe.
\p 
\v 8 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Niba anyangumbi ubin ru uz…õŐÉrh√£ h√£, umbi akpurha akp…Ēm igbong, niba akp…Ēmmbi ubingha, use ijara, use uhw…õk ri √≠bvuk atorhambi.
\v 9 √Äka atsu abadak b…Ēr niba akp…Ēmmbi atorho ak…Ē…Ē.
\v 10 Ub…õn iya umbi aka itsń©, √†ka asei um…Ē uts…õku unumkpi umbi aka isok ru uteu ha.
\v 11 Ub…õn anangk…õ umb…Ē aka asi iy…õimb…Ē umbi use aba asi ikpemb…Ē ato ru umbi, √†ka awashuwe uzurhu adakmbi ivangy…õ umbi aka isok, umgb…Ē uwu ideka iyiki ibewe ra atsimb…Ē.>>
\p 
\v 12 Umb…Ē adzek adzowe isarhe ug…õ anera adzipa.
\v 13 Umb…Ē atsusuwe √≠pfu iyiki ibewe √≠rh…õirh…õ, na adzukuwe atsei ra abi √≠rh√£rh√£ arh…õrh…õ akerhuwe umb…Ē.
\s1 Akpe Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima
