\v 24 Una h√£ adzek azń© arhusu uyanga ag…õ, <<Umum iwuri irhusu use?>>
\p Uyanga ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Itsi Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima.>>
\p 
\v 25 Kanying una h√£ abvui atń© azń©√£ ru uy…õrhe ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Umum ibee ic…õr…õ ungo udzaa itsi Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima ri it…õŐÉrhń©.>>
\p 
\v 26 Am…õn Uy…õrhe aghong akarh√£rh√£, b…Ēr uyirhnga aka ayirh ra asu atsennga, itsu unga asi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ak…õna unga.
\v 27 Nggee kanying unga adene und…Ēsu uy…õrhe akŇ© itsi Uyohana akŇ© aba. Utsa ha azń© azharhe itsi Uyohana ru ugborzń©.
\v 28 AkŇ© itsi ha ri it…õŐÉrhń© akŇ© aba. Adzowe ru una h√£, unga ay…õi adzowe ru uyanga.
\v 29 Angw…õŐÉ imesu Uyohana aka agŇ© isarhe ha, umb…Ē aba ashupu ukom Uyohana adzake.
\s1 Uyesu afuka anera anakag…Ēnga at…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ
\r (Umat 14.13-21; Irh 9.10-17; Uyoh 6.1-14)
\p 
\v 30 Uner itser Uyesu ak…Ēng adziir Uyesu na ad…õyiwe unga kishoo abink…õ umb…Ē aka akorhe na amesuwe.
\v 31 M…Ēc…õ, anera arh…õrh…õ aka anu iba na adzek uts…õku umb…Ē asi ikpomb…Ē ivang igha ubin, unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka aba nggu umum um…õn izń© ra anangk…õ anera aka ashimb…Ē um…Ē, um…õn iwosha ukunjiir.>>
\p 
\v 32 Nggee umb…Ē atsń© ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ azń©mb…Ē anangk…õ anera aka ashimb…Ē um…Ē.
\v 33 B…Ēr umb…Ē aka isoka anang h√£, anera arh…õrh…õ aka any√£ umb…Ē ahw…õngmb…Ē umb…Ē. Atń© ra adak adzeyi ri √≠teu kishoo, anggbaashia azń© atsń©mb…Ē ru umb…Ē.
\v 34 Uyesu aka acipa ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē any√£ arh…õrha anera aka ak…Ēng. Unga agŇ© atorh umb…Ē, ubinkutsu umb…Ē awu ru nyaki √≠d…Ēi iki ishingge ru uner idz…õu. Nggee unga atirha amesuwe umb…Ē abina arh…õrh…õ.
\p 
\v 35 Unum uku uyo itsitsń©, nggee angw…õŐÉ imesanga aba ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Anera ashimb…Ē ra anang ak…õr…õ, nggay…õ unum uku uwuri itsń©kp…Ē.
\v 36 Udene anera umb…Ē atsń© √≠teu nu √≠cang iyiki ikhapa nggimi agoi ubin umb…Ē aka igha.>>
\p 
\v 37 B…Ēr unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi √†ka adzowe umb…Ē ubin umb…Ē agha.>>
\p Um…Ē umb…Ē ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ug…õ um…õn izń© igoi ubingha ukpu imang uner itser af…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ut…Ēr…Ēk! Um…õn izń© if…õre imang iy…õr…õ ru ubingha ni idzowe umb…Ē agha?>>
\p 
\v 38 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi awu ra aborodi asong nggu umbi? √Äka azń© arhi.>>
\p Umb…Ē aka azń© arhi, umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Aborodi at…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ, nu ab…õrh avaa.>>
\p 
\v 39 Uyesu atsu umb…Ē ag…Ēr anera asei ukpukpusha nu ubń©ń© uku usum.
\v 40 Nggee umb…Ē asei ukpukpusha ab…Ē…Ē ananaka ab…Ē…Ē is…Ēka it…ĒŐÉit…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ.
\v 41 Unga aka anyangu aborodi ha ikit…ĒŐÉnake nu ab…õrh ha ikivarhake, aberi itsinga arhi af√£, atar uw…õ…õ na ats…Ēku uborodi ha. M…Ēc…õ unga adzise angw…õŐÉ imesanga umb…Ē akŇ© azń© adene anera. Ik…õi unga agashuwe ab…õrh ha ikivarhake ru umb…Ē kishoo.
\v 42 Kishoo agha, ashuurmb…Ē.
\v 43 Angw…õŐÉ imesa arh…ĒŐÉyń© awushu uborodi ha nu ab…õrh ha at…Ēk azń©nga us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn.
\v 44 Irh…õ anera aka agha ubingha ha, akatsak awu anakag…Ēnga at…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ.
\s1 Uyesu az…õŐÉrhŇ© uz…õŐÉrh√£ afaf√£ nu am…õŐÉ
\r (Umat 14.22-36; Uyoh 6.15-21)
\p 
\v 45 Kanying Uyesu atsu angw…õŐÉ imesanga atsń© ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ agbaashia azń© ugar Ubetsaida, na asoyiwe ikik…Ēnga.
\v 46 Unga aka asoyiwe umb…Ē amaa, unga afŇ©√£ igŇ© azń©√£ if…õn-Num.
\p 
\v 47 Urh…õ…õ uku uwe, ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ h√£ uwe ra ateu ukau, unga awu ikiyikanga nu abń©.
\v 48 Unga any√£ angw…õŐÉ imesanga at…õŐÉw√£ ikpikpayi, ugba uk…õnkp…Ē umb…Ē izń© ra asu. Utsar ukpu akara ataar aki utsuu unga azń©√£ ru umb…Ē, az…õŐÉrh√£ afaf√£ nu am…õŐÉ ukau ha. Unga abee ifara umb…Ē at…Ēng,
\v 49 b…Ēr umb…Ē aka any√£ unga az…õŐÉrh√£ afaf√£ nu ukau am…õŐÉ h√£, umb…Ē atsar ug…õ awu im√£rh√£. Umb…Ē atsu ivum,
\v 50 Umb…Ē aka any√£ unga, umb…Ē agbipa kishookamb…Ē.
\p Kanying unga arherhe arherhe nggu umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka aker am…õnmbi! Awu umum. Niba agŇ©mbi iwei!>>
\v 51 Unga atsń©√£ ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē nggu umb…Ē, m…Ēc…õ ugbaka ukpekp…Ē. Umb…Ē adzeidzeu akarh√£rh√£,
\v 52 umb…Ē asi ihw…õngmb…Ē agben aki ubingha ukpu inera anakag…Ēnga at…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ h√£, ubinkutsu, am…õnmb…Ē asi iy…õike.
\p 
\v 53 Umb…Ē aka agar ukau ha, umb…Ē acipa ra abń© Ujanisarat, abope ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ h√£ nu angwń© ukau ukug…Ēng h√£.
\v 54 Ub…õn umb…Ē aka adzek ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ h√£, kanying anera ahw…õngmb…Ē ug…õ awu Uyesu.
\v 55 Umb…Ē atń©na adzeyiwa ra abń©mb…Ē kishoo akŇ©na abi irh√£rh√£ ra afarmb…Ē akŇ© azń© kishoo ra anangk…õ Uyesu aka awe.
\v 56 Kishoo anangk…õ unga aka izń©, iteu iki ig…Ēng, use iteu iki ici, umb…Ē angw…õŐÉwe abi irh√£rh√£ ra angwń© anang iz…õ…õ. Na ash…ĒŐÉrh√£ unga ru abi irh√£rh√£ h√£ abangu ut…õm ibang atorhanga. Kishoo abirab…õ aka akpo ibibanga akerhumb…Ē.
\c 7
\s1 Ugau anggbaashi
\r (Umat 15.1-9)
\p 
\v 1 Abi Ufarisi nu ab…Ē…Ē abika amesuwe Ikpem aka adzeku Urusharhima aba ak…Ēng adziir Uyesu.
\v 2 Na any√£ angw…õŐÉ imesanga agha ubingha nggu abok arhim, asi isorhmb…Ē abokmb…Ē aka awu agbeyamb…Ē.
\p 
\v 3 Abi Ufarisi nggu abi Uyahuda kishoo aka isaka asorh abokmb…Ē akata na ad…Ērha agha ubingha, ubinkutsu awu ugau agbeyi akakŇ©mb…Ē.
\v 4 Ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka idzeki iz…õ…õ abvui aba ri iya, asi √≠ghamb…Ē ubin, umb…Ē awuri igbaashia ad…Ēsa agbeyamb…Ē asorh ayormb…Ē kata. Na asorh akp…õwa nu √≠dzum am…õŐÉ nu at…õŐÉrhń© nu andzoma nu atseu.
\p 
\v 5 Nggee abi Ufarisi nu abika amesuwe Ikpem arhusu Uyesu ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu angw…õŐÉ imesango asi id…Ēsumb…Ē ugau akakŇ© na anu igha abin nggu abok arhim?>>
\p 
\v 6 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Irhikungge Uishaya aka as…Ēm Arherhu-Num ra atsimbi abi ukpukpeta ag…õ,
\q1 << <Aner ab…õr…õ adzaa umum ig…Ēng ra angwń©,
\q2 b…Ēr am…õnmb…Ē aderke nggu umum.
\q1 
\v 7 Umb…Ē adzaa umum ig…Ēng ib…õm,
\q2 anu imesuwe ikpem anera ug…õ…õ Unum adzowe umb…Ē.>\f + \fr 7.7 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uish 29.13\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 8 <<Umbi aka atarkumbi ikpem Unum, umbi ad…Ēsa agau anera.>>
\p 
\v 9 Na ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi aka akpombi anang umbi aka angw…õŐÉwe Ikpem Unum ngge its√ļ umbi id…Ēsa agaumbi!
\v 10 Umusa ag…Ēr ag…õ, <Udzowe imor ru ut…õngo nu uyango,>\f + \fr 7.10 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Idzi 20.12; Iva 5.16\xt*\ft .\f* nu <Ik…õi, uwuruwi aka arhenu ut…õnga use uyanga, awu ufang umb…Ē af…õre unga.>\f + \fr 7.10 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Idzi 21.17; Urha 20.9\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 11 B…Ēr umbi aka isaka ag…Ēr ag…õ unera aba ag…Ēr ut…õnga use uyanga ag…õ, <Ubin h√£ uwu izŇ©w√£ iyi Unum.>
\v 12 Rimi h√£, umbi ak…õnmbi unga ikorhu ub…õn ubin ayike ut…õnga use uyanga.
\v 13 Rimi h√£ umbi af…ĒŐÉrhŇ©we Arherhu-Num na ad…Ēsa agbeyi ha umbi aki imesuwe angw…õŐÉmbi. Ik…õi umbi aki ikorhe abin arh…õrh…õ ru nyaka ha.>>
\s1 Abink…õ aki itsu unera asi isara
\r (Umat 15.10-20)
\p 
\v 14 Ik…õi Uyesu ayisu ikik…Ēng h√£ iba ru unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Ub…õn unera akpeto ru umum, aka ahw…õng ak…õr…õ.
\v 15 Asi iwea abin awiya aki itsń© ru unera atsu unga asi isara, abink…õ aka idzeyiwa ra am…õn unera atsu unga asi isara ra asu Unum.>>\f + \fr 7.15 \ft Abvur ak…Ē…Ē aki its…õng abok aki isha ag…Ērke ik…õi ug…õ, \fv 16\fqa Kishoo uner ato aka agŇ©, unga agŇ©!\f*
\p 
\v 17 Unga aka asok ri ikik…Ēng h√£ na atsń©√£ ri iya, angw…õŐÉ imesanga arhusa unga agben unyaka arherhe ha.
\v 18 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi adzuna? Umbi asi ihw…õngmbi ug…õ abink…õ aka adzeka awiya atsń© ru unera asi √≠tsu unga asi isara ra asu Unum?
\v 19 Abin h√£ asi itsń©ke ra am…õnnga b…Ēr atsń© ra anaanga, na adzek ri iyornga.>> Ra arherhe ak…õr…õ Uyesu ad…õyiwe ug…õ abingha kishoo awu asarsatake.
\p 
\v 20 Ag…õ, <<Ubinkpi iki idzeyiwa ra am…õn unera awu ukp…Ē utsu unga asi isara ra asu Unum.
\v 21 Ubinkutsu iwu ru un…Ērkang am…õn unera, if…õrhk…Ē iyiki ibewe iki idzeyiwa, arhim irha ukuts…õrh use ukutsak, nu iv…õu, nu if…õr uner nu itoma-dak,
\v 22 nu ikpona, nu iyiki ibewe, nu irhirh…õm, nu any…Ēna, nu uny…õŐÉ…õŐÉ nu idakuwe itsok, nu iberi itsi nu ibemitsi, nu ik…õi ishera am…õn.
\v 23 Kishoo abin aka abewe ak…õr…õ adzeyiwa ra am…õn unera, ake atsu unera asi isara ra asu Unum.>>
\s1 Imangmang uts…õrh uw…Ē…Ē
\r (Umat 15.21-28)
\p 
\v 24 Uyesu ab…Ēruka anang h√£ na asok azń©√£ abń© Utaya nu Usidon. Atsń© ri iya ik…Ē…Ē asi ibeenga unera ahw…õng, rimi h√£ unga af…Ēr iwiwoi adaka.
\v 25 Idzidz…õrhe, kanying uts…õrh uw…Ē…Ē, uwuruwi ungw…õŐÉrhŇ© unapunga aka awe ru ipfu iyiki ibewe aka agŇ© isarhe ri itsinga, aba agba ra adaknga.
\v 26 Awu uts…õrh abń© Uherhini, amar unga udiku ugb…õr uwu Ufinikiya. Unga ash…ĒŐÉrhŇ© Uyesu ama atsŇ©we ipfu iyiki ibewe ru unapunga.
\p 
\v 27 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Uneke aw…õkaci agbaashia agha kishoo ubinkpi umb…Ē aka abee, ubinkutsu isi irhikungge umb…Ē anyangu ubingha aw…õkaci atsuke √≠jui.>>
\p 
\v 28 B…Ēr uts…õrh ha ag…õ, <<ń®ń©, Uteijee, b…Ēr ru adak utebur √≠jui iki isaki ighangge awushu ubingha aka idze ra abok aw…õkaci agbei.>>
\p 
\v 29 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Iwu idzidz…õrhe, uzń© ri iya, ipfu iyiki ibewe iki idzengge ru unapungo.>>
\p 
\v 30 Unga abvui azń© ri iya any√£ unapa anu nu ukoma, ipfu iyiki ibewe iki idzengge ru unga.
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe ugbau uwuku // uf…Ēr arherhe adaka
\p 
\v 31 M…Ēc…õ Uyesu adzek udiku ugb…õr Utaya ad…Ēsu udiku Usidon, azń©√£ Ukau Ugarhirhi nu utsń©ndń© uku uzń© iteu us…Ēka umb…Ē iki iyisa Udikaforhi.
\v 32 Ngg…Ē…Ē ha umb…Ē aka akowe unga uner igbau uwuku uf…Ēr arherhe adaka, umb…Ē ash…ĒŐÉrh√£ unga atsorhu ubok nu uner ha.
\p 
\v 33 Nggee Uyesu adarhu uner igbau ha akŇ© azń©√£, adzeka ri ikik…Ēng h√£, atsu itoknga ra ato utsak ha. Unga atar aci akŇ© abanguwe arh…õm utsak ha.
\v 34 Na abere arhi afaf√£ agbiir uwoi ughorghotakp…Ē, ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Iffata!>> Agbena ag…õ, <<Uyanga!>>
\v 35 Kanying unga aka arherhe rimi, ato utsak ha ayanga, urh…õmnga ugarhe unga atirhunga arherhe azezee.
\p 
\v 36 Uyesu atsu umb…Ē niba ad…õyikumb…Ē unera. B…Ēr ub…õn unga aka ik…õn umb…Ē, umb…Ē anang ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ is…Ēme anera.
\v 37 Anera agŇ© na adzeidzeu kishoo ag…õ, <<Heee! Akorhe ub…õn abina azezerake. Atsu ugbau agŇ©√£ arherhe, uwuku uf…Ēr arherhe, arherhe azezee.>>
\c 8
\s1 Uyesu afuka anera anaka ag…Ēnga anaa
\r (Umat 15.32-39)
\p 
\v 1 Ri inum h√£ anera ab…Ē…Ē arh…õrh…õ ak…Ēng. Umb…Ē aka ashimb…Ē ru ubinkpi umb…Ē aka igha, Uyesu ayisa angw…õŐÉ imesanga umb…Ē azń© ru unga na ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ,
\v 2 <<Umum igŇ© atorh anera ab…õr…õ. Unum untaar nukpi umb…Ē awu nggu umum na ashimb…Ē ru ubingha.
\v 3 Umum ń©ba isoyikŇ© umb…Ē azń© ri iya nggu imerh, umb…Ē awuri igbamb…Ē nu utsń©ndń©, ubinkutsu ab…Ē…Ē adzeki inang iyiki ider.>>
\p 
\v 4 Angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Um…õn √≠ny√£ ubingha ri in…õ…õ ukpu um…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ighigha anera ab…õr…õ ra arhum ak…õr…õ?>>
\p 
\v 5 Uyesu arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi awe ru √≠po uborodi isong?>>
\p Umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Ut…Ē…Ēva.>>
\p 
\v 6 Unga ag…Ēr ikik…Ēng h√£ iseisa abń©. Ivangy…õ unga aka anyangu aborodi ha ut…Ē…Ēva, atar uw…õ…õ ru Unum, na ats…Ēka ake agasha adzise angw…õŐÉ imesa umb…Ē adene ru anera, umb…Ē akorhe rimi h√£.
\v 7 Umb…Ē awemb…Ē ru angw…õŐÉrh√£ ab…õrh ukunjiir, unga atar uw…õ…õ ra ake ik…õi, unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē agashuwe ikik…Ēnga.
\v 8 Anera agha ashur, angw…õŐÉ imesa arh…ĒŐÉń© akika abub…Ēr ake at…Ēk azń©nga ut…Ē…Ēva.
\v 9 Irh…õ anera aka agha, atsń©mb…Ē anaka ag…Ēnga anaa. M…Ēc…õ Uyesu asoyika anera umb…Ē azń©mb…Ē.
\v 10 Kanying unga atsń© ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ nu angw…õŐÉ imesanga, azń©√£ abń© Udarhmanuta.
\s1 Ibee atsar
\r (Umat 16.1-4; Irh 12.54-56)
\p 
\v 11 Abi Ufarisi ab…Ē…Ē aba atirhi uning nggu Uyesu. Avira unga, umb…Ē abee unga akorhuwe abin idzeu ake awu utsar ug…õ unga adzeka af√£.
\v 12 Unga agb…õr usepa ughoghor na ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu umbi aner undan ukpir…õ abee iny√£ atsar? Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, utsar ushikp…Ē umb…Ē aka id…õyiwe ukp…Ē.>>
\v 13 M…Ēc…õ unga ab…Ēruka umb…Ē, atsń© ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ, agar azń©√£ ugar ukp…Ēr…Ē.
\s1 Uguga abi Ufarisi nu Uhiridu
\r (Umat 16.5-12)
\p 
\v 14 Angw…õŐÉ imesu Uyesu ayirukumb…Ē asi ikŇ©mb…Ē uborodi. Akpurha awe ru ipoa unying ukpekŇ© ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ h√£.
\v 15 Uyesu agbiite atomb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka akp…Ēm am…õnmbi nggu uga abi Ufarisi nu uwu Uhiridu.>>
\p 
\v 16 Angw…õŐÉ imesa ha atirhi irherhe nggu ad…Ēka ag…õ, <<Arherhe rimi ubinkutsu um…õn iki isi ikŇ©m…õn uborodi.>>
\p 
\v 17 Unga ahw…õng arherhak…õ umb…Ē aka arherhe, unga arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu umbi anu ig…Ēr ug…õ umbi ashimbi ru uborodi? Uts…õku ic…õr…õ umbi asi iny√£ ahw…õngmbi? Am…õnmbi awe ru igbau?
\v 18 Umbi awu ra asu na asi iny√£mbi, na awembi ra ato na asi igŇ©mbi? Umbi asi iyitumbi,
\v 19 ivangy…õ umum iki igashuwe anera anaka ag…Ēnga at…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ nggu aborodi at…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ? Azń©nga asong umbi aka akarha akika ab…Ēr?>>
\p Umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn.>>
\p 
\v 20 <<Ivangy…õ umum iki its…Ēku ipo aborodi ut…Ē…Ēva ha, umum iki igashuwe anera anaka ag…Ēnga anaa, azń©ng akag…Ēng asong umbi aka akarha at…Ēk?>>
\p Umb…Ē ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ut…Ē…Ēva.>>
\p 
\v 21 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Uts…õku ic…õr…õ umbi asi ihw…õngmbi?>>
\s1 Akerhuwe uner ibvuta ru Ubetsaida
\p 
\v 22 Umb…Ē aka aba Ubetsaida, ab…Ē…Ē akŇ© uner ibvuta ash…ĒŐÉrhŇ© Uyesu abangu uner ibvuta ha.
\v 23 Unga adzur ubok uner ibvuta ha akŇ©na unga adzek azń©√£ undzing utepa. Ivangy…õ unga aka ashapa aci ra asu utsak ha na atsorhu ubok nu unga, Uyesu arhusa ag…õ, <<Ungo ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉ uny√£…Ē ubin ukp…Ē…Ē?>>
\p 
\v 24 Unga abera asunga na ag…õ, <<Iny√£mum anera, umb…Ē awu ru nyaka acucii iki iz…õŐÉrh√£.>>
\p 
\v 25 Uyesu abvui abanga asu utsak ha. M…Ēc…õ utsak ha ayangi ikpor asunga ugeii, asunga akerhuke, unga any√£ abina uku ushashaki.
\v 26 Uyesu adene unga azń©√£ ri iya, ag…õ, <<Niba ubvui uzń©…Ē udiku utepa.>>
\s1 Ubitru adeku Uyesu unga awu Ukiristo
\r (Umat 16.13-20; Irh 9.18-21)
\p 
\v 27 Uyesu nggu angw…õŐÉ imesanga azń©mb…Ē, atsń©rhń© iteu iki ici iyi Ukaisariya Ufirhibi. Nu utsń©ndń© unga arhusa angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<Anera anu ig…Ēr ag…õ umum iwu ungam…Ē?>>
\p 
\v 28 Umb…Ē ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ab…Ē…Ē ag…õ ungo uwu Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima, ab…Ē…Ē ag…õ, ungo uwu uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uirhiya, ab…Ē…Ē ag…õ ungo uwu unying ra abika as…Ēm Arherhu-Num.>>
\p 
\v 29 Unga arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<B…Ēr umbi ag…Ēr ug…õ umum iwu ungam…Ē?>> Ubitru ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ungo uwu Ukiristo.>>
\p 
\v 30 Uyesu agbiite atomb…Ē utsur umb…Ē ad…õyikumb…Ē unera ubinkpi unga aka awe.
\s1 Uyesu as…Ēm ikpŇ© akpek…õ // unga aka ikpe
\r (Umat 16.21-28; Irh 9.22-27)
\p 
\v 31 Unga atirha amesuwe umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner awuri ihwa uver ra abina arh…õrh…õ nu akakŇ© nu ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num, nu abika amesuwe Ikpem, awuri ikp…õŐÉmb…Ē unga. Awuri if…õre unga, ru unum untaar unga awuri isoka nggu urh…õ.>>
\v 32 Arherhe ak…õr…õ ha ra awiya. Nggee Ubitru adarha unga azń© ri if…õna atirhi its…õrha unga.
\p 
\v 33 B…Ēr Uyesu adzipa arhi angw…õŐÉ imesa ha, ats…õrhu Ubitru ag…õ, <<Us…Ēk…Ē ru umum Ushaitan! Ungo uwu utarh ukpuku ukw…õr itok ru umum, if…õrhk…Ēngo iwe ru nyaki iyi anera, isi iwengge ru nyaki iyi Unum.>>
\p 
\v 34 M…Ēc…õ unga ayisa anera nu angw…õŐÉ imesanga aba ru unga, unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Unera aba abeenga id…Ēsa umum, awu ufang unga akp…õŐÉ…õŐÉ itsinga na ashipu ig√£rh√£mau ucuciianga ad…Ēsa umum.
\v 35 Ub…õn unerwi aka abee if…Ērh urh…õnga, umgb…Ē uwuri igwir, b…Ēr uwuku ugwirhuwe urh…õnga ru ubokmum nu Isarhe Iyiki Ize afuf…Ērh umgb…Ē.
\v 36 Izea iwu use unera akpo abin upfung kishoo na asi ikpoa urh…õnga?
\v 37 Use unera awuri ikŇ© use ukp…Ē uwe ifare urh…õnga?
\v 38 Unera aba agŇ©√£ atsakmum nu arherhamum ru udan ukpuku ushe irhirhika ukpir…õ ukpu itoma-dak nu arhim, Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner awuri igigŇ©a atsak uner ha ri ivangy…õ unga aka iba ri ikpikpoi Ut…õnga nggu √≠pfu itser-Num isarsatangge.>>
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, ab…Ē…Ē rab…Ē ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ nggimi awuri iny√£mb…Ē ijee Iy…õrhe af√£ kata na ad…Ērha akpe.>>
\s1 Idzidzipu iyor Uyesu
\r (Umat 17.1-13; Irh 9.28-36)
\p 
\v 2 Inuma ut…ĒŐÉń© iki imaa Uyesu akŇ© Ubitru, nu Uyaku, nu Uyohana, afŇ© igŇ© iyiki ider ikiyikamb…Ē. Um…Ē iyor Uyesu idzipa iwiwengge ra asumb…Ē.
\v 3 Atorhanga ik…õi awu akaterha uku up…õŐÉrh…õŐÉng uku unyar-nyar, anangke isisorh unera ru upfung ukpir…õ.
\v 4 M…Ēc…õ abika as…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uirhiya nu Umusa akap…õng ra asumb…Ē, ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ arherhe nggu Uyesu.
\p 
\v 5 Ubitru ag…Ēr Uyesu ag…õ, <<A umarhem, azea um…õn iki iwe ri nggimi, uneke um…õn itar atsurha ataar, unying uwu ungo, unying uwu Umusa, unying uwu Uirhiya.>>
\v 6 Unga asi ihw…õngnga ubinkpi unga aka arherhe, ubinkutsu umb…Ē agŇ© iwei akarh√£rh√£.
\p 
\v 7 M…Ēc…õ am…õ…õ adzek aba atsire umb…Ē, urh…õm udzek ra am…õ…õ ha, ug…Ēr ug…õ, <<Uw…õr…õ awu Ungw…õŐÉmum, uwu umum iki ibema. √Äka akpe ato ru unga!>>
\p 
\v 8 Kanying, umb…Ē aka arhi adzipa, asi iny√£mb…Ē unera akpurha any√£ Uyesu ikiyikanga nggu umb…Ē.
\p 
\v 9 Umb…Ē aka az…õŐÉrh√£ acipuwa ru igŇ© h√£, Uyesu agbiite atomb…Ē ug…õ niba ad…õyikumb…Ē unera ubinkpi umb…Ē aka any√£ uts…õku Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner aka isoka akpe.
\v 10 Ngge itsu umb…Ē angw…õŐÉ arherhe ha ra am…õnmb…Ē, na arhusa ad…Ēkamb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use uwu agben isoka akpe?>>
\p 
\v 11 Umb…Ē arhusa unga ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu abika amesuwe Ikpem anu ig…Ēr ug…õ awu ufang uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uirhiya agbaashia aba?>>
\p 
\v 12 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu idzidz…õrhe Uirhiya agbaashia aba agbishi if…õrh…õ kishoo. Awu use utsu its…õng ig…Ēr ig…õ awu ufang Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner ahwa uver urh…õrh…õ umb…Ē akp…õŐÉmb…Ē unga?
\v 13 B…Ēr umum ind…õyiwa umbi Uirhiya aka abanga, anera akorhuwe unga ubinkpi umb…Ē aka abee, ru nyaka ngge iki its…õng ri itsinga.>>
\s1 Ikikerhe uw…õkuci uwu // ipfu iyiki ibewe
\r (Umat 17.14-23; Irh 9.37-45)
\p 
\v 14 Uyesu nggu angw…õŐÉ imesanga h√£ ikitatamb…Ē abvui aba ra angw…õŐÉ imesanga, umb…Ē any√£ nggaa ikik…Ēng iki idzipa umb…Ē nu abika amesuwe Ikpem ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ uning nggu umb…Ē.
\v 15 Kanying umb…Ē aka any√£ Uyesu, kishoo ikik…Ēng h√£ idzedzeu akarh√£rh√£, asok atń©tser azń© aghwe unga.
\p 
\v 16 Uyesu arhusa angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<Umbi ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ uning use nggu umb…Ē?>>
\p 
\v 17 Uner uw…Ē…Ē ri ikik…Ēng h√£ adzipuwe ag…õ, <<A umarhem, nggawi umum ikŇ©w√£ ungo ungw…õŐÉmum, uwuruwi aka awe ru ipfu iyiki ibewe iki ik…õnngge unga arherhe.
\v 18 Ivangy…õ ngge iki isok ru unga, iki isaki itare unga ra abń©. Itsu unga adzeyi ufuu ra angwń©nga, anu ishang anyń©, iyornga id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ikerketangge. Umum ń©g…Ēr angw…õŐÉ imesango ama atsŇ©we, b…Ēr umb…Ē af…Ēr adamb…Ē.>>
\p 
\v 19 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi abi udan ukpir…õ, abika asheri imangmang, abi am…õn aka abewe. Umum iki isei ń©d√£rhŇ©mum nggu umbi, ukang umbi aka awe ru imangmang ru umum? Uts…õku ukang umum iki ibima nggu ida imangmangmbi? UkŇ© ungw…õŐÉ h√£ uba ngg…õ…õ ru umum.>>
\p 
\v 20 Nggee umb…Ē akŇ© unga aba. Ivangy…õ ipfu iyiki ibewe iki iny√£ Uyesu, kanying ngge ikw…õr ungw…õŐÉ h√£ iyornga izang. Unga agba ag…ĒŐÉrh√£, ufuu ik…õi udzeyi ra angwń©nga.
\p 
\v 21 Uyesu arhusu ut…õ ungw…õŐÉ h√£ ag…õ, <<Ukang if…õrh…õ ha iki itirhi ru unga?>>
\p Ut…õ ungw…õŐÉ h√£ ag…õ, <<Itirhi unga ana awu uw…õkuci ukunjiir.
\v 22 Iki isaki itare unga ru urha, nu am…õŐÉ, ibee if…õre unga. B…Ēr ungo uba ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ukorhuk…Ē ubin, uma ugŇ© atorh um…õn uma uyika um…õn.>>
\p 
\v 23 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu ungo urhusa ug…õ umum ń©ba id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ im…õŐÉmum? Ub…õn if…õrh…õ iwengge ru uwuruwi aka awe ru imangmang.>>
\p 
\v 24 Kanying ut…õ ungw…õŐÉ h√£ atsarhi irhaknga ag…õ, <<Umum iwemum ri imangmang, uma uyika umum ingbiki iwerangge!>>
\p 
\v 25 Uyesu aka any√£ ikik…Ēng h√£ iki itń© iba, unga ats…õrhi ipfu iyiki ibewe ha ag…õ, <<Ungo ipfu iyiki ibewe iyiki itsu igbau ni ik…õn arherhe, umum itsu ungo upfudzek ru unga, niba ubvui utsń©…ĒŐÉ ru unga ik…õi!>>
\p 
\v 26 Ipfu iyiki ibewe ha itsu ivum, izung ungw…õŐÉ h√£ m…Ēc…õ ngge idzekngge. Ungw…õŐÉ h√£ anu ru nyaku ukom, nggee irh…õ anera ig…Ēr ug…õ, <<Aka akpea.>>
\v 27 B…Ēr Uyesu adzur uboknga aberuwe unga nu adaknga, unga asok ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ.
\p 
\v 28 Uyesu aka atsń© ri iya, angw…õŐÉ imesanga arhusa unga ikiyikamb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu um…õn isi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ itsŇ©wŇ©kum…õn ipfu iyiki ibewe ha?>>
\p 
\v 29 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<IkpŇ© idzidzek iy…õr…õ iwuri iwe ri if…õn-Num ukpekŇ©.>>
\p 
\v 30 Umb…Ē asokmb…Ē ra anang h√£, az…õŐÉrh√£ at…Ēng ru Ugarhirhi. Uyesu asi ibeenga anera ahw…õng anangk…õ umb…Ē aka awe,
\v 31 ubinkutsu anu imesuwe angw…õŐÉ imesanga. Ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awuri ighamb…Ē adak Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner adzowe unga ra abok anera. Umb…Ē awuri if…õre unga, inuma itaar iki it…Ēng unga awuri isoka.>>
\v 32 B…Ēr umb…Ē asi ihw…õngmb…Ē agben arherhanga, na agŇ© iwei irhusa unga.
\s1 Ungaa awu uwuku ug…Ēnga?
\r (Umat 18.1-5; Irh 9.46-48)
\p 
\v 33 Ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka azń© atsń© Ukafanahum, ivangy…õ unga aka awe ri iya, unga arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ uning use ru utsń©ndń©?>>
\v 34 B…Ēr umb…Ē anukutata, ubinkutsu nu utsń©ndń© umb…Ē ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ uning ug…õ ungaa awu uwuku ug…Ēnga ru umb…Ē.
\p 
\v 35 Uyesu asei, na ayisa umb…Ē us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£, ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Ub…õn unera aka abee iwu ukug…Ēngmbi, awu ufang unga awu uwuku ucia, ik…õi na awu ug√£rh√£mbi kishoo.>>
\p 
\v 36 Unga ashupu ungw…õŐÉrhŇ© uw…õkuci atsu unga ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ra ateumb…Ē. Unga ashupa unga awuma ra aboknga, ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ,
\v 37 <<Uwuku uy…õi ungw…õŐÉrhŇ© uw…õkuci ru nyaku uw…õr…õ ri itsokmum, ay…õi umum nukp…Ē, uwuruwi aka ay…õi umum ay…õi uwuku udena umum ń©ba.>>
\s1 Uwuruwi aka asi ikp…õŐÉ…õŐÉ um…õn // awu uwu um…õn
\r (Irh 9.49-50)
\p 
\v 38 Uyohana ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A umarhem, um…õn iny√£ uner uw…Ē…Ē anu itsusuwe ipfu iyiki ibewe ri itsokngo, um…õn ik…õnm…õn unga, ubinkutsu asi iwea nggu um…õn.>>
\p 
\v 39 B…Ēr Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<√Äka niba ak…õnmbi unga. Unera asi √≠korhunga ubin idzeu ri itsokmum amaa na arherhunga iki ibewe ri itsimum.
\v 40 Ub…õn unerwi aka asi ikp…õŐÉ…õŐÉ um…õn awu uwu um…õn.
\v 41 Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, kishoo uwuku udzaa umbi ukp…õwa am…õŐÉ aka ahwa ri itsokmum ug…õ umbi awu abi Ukiristo, umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe awuri ikpoa ugb…õtanga.
\s1 Abin aka itsu igbigba ra arhim
\r (Umat 18.6-9; Irh 17.1-2)
\p 
\v 42 <<Ub…õn uwuruwi aka itsu unying ra aw…õkaci abika awe ru imangmang ru umum agba ra arhim, ugba umb…Ē abope uk…Ē ig…Ē ru urh…Ēk uner ha na atsuke unga ru ukau ukug…Ēng.
\v 43 Ubokngo uba utsu ungo ugba…Ē ra arhim, uzharhuwe ukp…Ē. Azea ungo utsń© urh…õ uwu ugbagbaa nggu uboka unying nu ungo uku ineke abokngo ikivarhake atsń© idzŇ© urhakpi uku usi √≠rhimkp…Ē.\f + \fr 9.43 \ft Abvur ak…Ē…Ē aki its…õng abok aki isha ag…Ērke ik…õi ug…õ, \fv 44\fqa Ra anangk…õ adzudzi iki igha, ake asi √≠kpeke, urha ik…õi usi √≠rhimkp…Ē.\f*
\v 45 Udakngo uba utsu ungo igba ra arhim, uzharhuwe ukp…Ē. Azea ungo utsń© urh…õ uwu ugbagbaa nggu igbeta nu ungo iki itsń© idzŇ© urhakpi uku usi √≠rhimkp…Ē nggu adakngo avaa.\f + \fr 9.45 \ft Abvur ak…Ē…Ē aki its…õng abok aki isha ag…Ērke ik…õi ug…õ, \fv 46\fqa Ra anangk…õ adzudzi iki igha, ake asi √≠kpeke, urha ik…õi usi √≠rhimkp…Ē.\f*
\v 47 Ishaa usungo iba itsu ungo ugba ra arhim, uhoote ukp…Ē. Azea ungo utsń© Iy…õrhe Unum nggu usua unying nu ungo uku itsń© ri idzŇ© urha nggu asu avaa.
\v 48 Um…Ē,
\q1 << <Adzudzimb…Ē asi √≠kpeke,
\q2 nu urha ik…õi usi √≠rhimkp…Ē.>\f + \fr 9.48 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uish 66.24\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 49 <<Asare anera kishoo nggu urha ru nyaka umb…Ē aka ikŇ© angw√£ asare id…õm.
\p 
\v 50 <<Angw√£ aze, b…Ēr ake aba ashike ri itonga angw√£, ungo ukorhu uguse nu utsu ake atonga ik…õi? √Äka awe ra angw√£ ra atsimbi, na asei uku ughw…Ē…Ēw nggu ad…Ēka.>>
\c 10
\s1 Igau its…õrh
\r (Umat 19.1-12; Irh 16.18)
\p 
\v 1 M…Ēc…õ Uyesu asoka ra anang h√£ na azń©√£ ugb…õr uwu Uyahudiya agar Az…õŐÉ Urdun. Ik…õi anera arh…õrh…õ abvui ak…Ēng ru unga, unga amesuwe umb…Ē ru nyaka unga aka abayi.
\p 
\v 2 Abi Ufarisi ab…Ē…Ē aba avira unga, arhusa ag…õ, <<Ri Ikpem im…õŐÉngge unera agau nggu uts…õŐÉnga?>>
\p 
\v 3 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umusa atsu umbi akorhu use?>>
\p 
\v 4 Umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umusa ag…Ēr um…õn ag…õ unera awuri id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ats…õng ubvur igau its…õrh awayika uts…õŐÉnga.>>
\p 
\v 5 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Its√£ itsimbi itsu Umusa ats…õnga umbi ak…õr…õ ha.
\v 6 B…Ēr ri inggbaashia <Unum amuna umb…Ē ukutsak nggu ukuts…õrh.>\f + \fr 10.6 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Ing 1.27\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 7 <Nggee, unera awuri ineke ut…õnga nu uyanga, na anyapa nggu uts…õŐÉnga.
\v 8 Umb…Ē ikivarhamb…Ē awuri iwu iyora unying.>\f + \fr 10.8 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Ing 2.24\xt*\ft .\f* Nggee umb…Ē asi iwemb…Ē ivaa b…Ēr awu iyora unying.
\v 9 Nggee, ubinkpi Unum aka agbopa, unera niba agashuka.>>
\p 
\v 10 Ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka awu ri iya, ik…õi, angw…õŐÉ imesa arhusu Uyesu arherhe ha.
\v 11 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Ub…õn uwuku ugau its…õrh nggu uts…õŐÉnga na apfunu uts…õrh uwukuse, unga awu ra arhim itoma-dak ru unga.
\v 12 Iwe rimi h√£ ukuts…õrh aba agau its…õrh nggu utsaka, na azń© its…õrh uner uwukuse, unga atoma-dak.>>
\s1 Angw…õŐÉrh√£ aw…õkaci nu Uyesu
\r (Umat 19.13-15; Irh 18.15-17)
\p 
\v 13 Anera aka akŇ© angw…õŐÉrh√£ aw…õkaci aba ru Uyesu abanga umb…Ē, b…Ēr angw…õŐÉ imesanga ats…õrha umb…Ē.
\v 14 Uyesu aka any√£ rimi, av…Ēm af…õr unga. Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka aneke angw…õŐÉrh√£ aw…õkaci aba ru umum, niba ak…õnmbi umb…Ē, Iy…õrhe-Num iwu iyi ikpŇ©mb…Ē.
\v 15 Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, ub…õn unera aka asi iy…õisa Iy…õrhe-Num ru nyaku uw…õkuci, asi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉ atsń©√£ ri ngge.>>
\v 16 M…Ēc…õ unga ashupa aw…õkaci ha ra aboknga awuma na atsorhe abok nu atsimb…Ē na atsuke umb…Ē idorh.
\s1 Uw…õdz…õm uner ubin
\r (Umat 19.16-30; Irh 18.18-30)
\p 
\v 17 Uyesu atirhi isisok ra anang h√£ nukpi, utsak uw…Ē…Ē atń© aba, atararhu ra anangnga, arhusa unga ag…õ. <<A umarhem uwuku uze, umum ikorhu use ni ikpo urh…õ uwu ugbagbaa?>>
\p 
\v 18 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu ungo uyisa umum uwuku uze? Uwuku uze ashia, Unum ukpekŇ© awu uwuku uze.
\v 19 Ungo uhw…õngo √≠kpem iy…õr…õ, <Niba uf…õr…Ē unera, niba utomungo-dak, niba uv…õp…Ē iv…õu, niba ugb…õr…Ē angwń© utsukuk…Ē unera, niba ugha…Ē urha, udzowe ig…Ēng ru ut…õngo nu uyango.>\f + \fr 10.19 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Idzi 20.12; Iva 5.16-20\xt*\ft .\f*>>
\p 
\v 20 Uw…õdz…õm h√£ ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A umarhem, umum iki id…Ēsumum ak…õr…õ ha kishoo rim…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ utirhi ri iw…õŐÉnci.>>
\p 
\v 21 Uyesu arhi unga na abema unga, ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ungo usheru ubina unying ukpekŇ©. Uzń©, ugoshe abinngo kishoo, udzowe uhw…õka ra atsŇ©w√£, ungo uwuri iwe…Ē ru ugb…õta urh…õrh…õ ra af√£, m…Ēc…õ uba ud…Ēsa umum.>>
\p 
\v 22 IgŇ© rimi itsu ungw…õŐÉdz…õm h√£ ashepa asunga, azń© nggu ida am…õn, ubinkutsu unga awu uner ubin akarh√£rh√£.
\p 
\v 23 Uyesu arhi adziir angw…õŐÉ imesanga, ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Aghong abika awu ru ubin aki ikpo itsń© Iy…õrhe Unum!>>
\p 
\v 24 Angw…õŐÉ imesanga adzeidzeu ra arherha ha. Uyesu ik…õi ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi aw…õkaci, aghong akarh√£rh√£ unera atsń© ri Iy…õrhe Unum!
\v 25 Igh…Ērhungge urhakumi utsń© at…Ēng ra angwń© inepurha, nu uner ubin aka itsń© ri Iy…õrhe Unum.>>
\p 
\v 26 Angw…õŐÉ imesa ha adzeidzeu akarh√£rh√£ arhusa ad…Ēka ag…õ, <<Ungam…Ē awuri id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ akpo ifif…Ērh?>>
\p 
\v 27 Uyesu arhi umb…Ē na ag…õ, <<Ra anera ngge isi √≠m…õŐÉngge, b…Ēr ru Unum im…õŐÉngge. Ub…õn ubina um…õŐÉ…õŐÉkp…Ē ra anang Unum.>>
\p 
\v 28 Ubitru ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Nggay…õ um…õn ineke abina kishoo ni ad…Ēsa ungo!>>
\p 
\v 29 Uyesu ag…õ, <<Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, unera ashia uwuruwi aka neke iyanga, use angw…õŐÉmb…Ē use anapumb…Ē use uyanga use ut…õnga use aw…õkacinga use icang irhamnga ri itsimum nu Isarhe Iyiki Ize,
\v 30 na asi ikpoa iya, angw…õŐÉmb…Ē, anapumb…Ē, uya, aw…õkaci nu icang irham idikunga unaka ru udan ukpir…õ, unga ikpoa uver ik…õi, ru upfung ukpuku uba unga ikpoa urh…õ uwu ugbagbaa.
\v 31 B…Ēr anera arh…õrh…õ aka awu abi inggbaashi, awuri iwu √£maata. √Émaata ik…õi, awuri iwu anggbaashi.>>
\s1 Uyesu abvui arherha arherhe // ra akpek…õ unga aka ikpe
\r (Umat 20.17-19; Irh 18.31-34)
\p 
\v 32 Umb…Ē awu ru utsń©ndń© uwuku afŇ©rh√£ azń© Urusharhima. Uyesu agbaashia nu udń© h√£. Angw…õŐÉ imesa adzeidzeu, nu abika ad…Ēsa unga agŇ© iwei. Ik…õi unga ayisa angw…õŐÉ imesanga us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£ ri ibanga ad…õyiwe umb…Ē ubinkpi iki ikorhe nggu unga.
\v 33 <<Nggay…õ um…õn izń© uf√£ Urusharhima. Um…Ē awuri ighamb…Ē adak Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner adzowe unga ra abok ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num, na abika amesuwe Ikpem. Awuri itsu unga ufai akpe na adzowe unga ra atsen abi Uyahuda.
\v 34 Umb…Ē awuri iy…õia unga na ashau aci atsuke ra asunga, awuri ikw…õre unga ugw…õ…õ na af…õre unga. Inuma itaar iki it…Ēng unga awuri isoka nggu urh…õ.>>
\s1 Ubinkpi Uyaku nu Uyohana aka af…õna
\r (Umat 20.20-28)
\p 
\v 35 M…Ēc…õ angw…õŐÉ Uzabadi, Uyaku nu Uyohana, aba ru unga. Ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A umarhem, um…õn ibee ungo ukorhuwa ub…õn ubina um…õn iki if…õna ungo.>>
\p 
\v 36 Unga arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi abee umum ikorhuwa umbi use?>>
\p 
\v 37 Umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Um…õn ish…ĒŐÉrh√£ ungo neke unying ru um…õn asei n√ļ ubok ughango, uwu uvaa asei n√ļ ubok uferango ri ikpikpoingo.>>
\p 
\v 38 B…Ēr Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi asi ihw…õngmbi ubinkpi umbi aka arhusa. Umbi awuri id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ahwambi ru ukp…õwa uverkpi umum iki ihwa, use umbi awuri id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ akorhumbi ikpŇ© ub…Ētisima uverkpi umb…Ē aka ikorhuwa umum?>>
\p 
\v 39 Umb…Ē ag…õ, <<ń®ń©, um…õn id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ikorhum…õn.>> Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<ń®ń©, umbi awuri ihwambi ru ukp…õwa umum iki ihwa na awuri akorhumbi ub…Ētisima h√£ umb…Ē aka ikorhuwa umum,
\v 40 b…Ēr isei nu ubok ughamum use ubok uferamum asi iwea umum ń©bemuwa. Inang iy…õr…õ iwu iyi abirab…õ umb…Ē aka as…õng agbishuwe rim…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ.>>
\p 
\v 41 Ivangy…õ angw…õŐÉ imesa ha us…Ēka aka agŇ© rimi, umb…Ē agŇ© av…Ēm nggu Uyaku nu Uyohana.
\v 42 Uyesu ayisa umb…Ē ananga unying ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi ahw…õngmbi ug…õ abirab…õ umb…Ē aka anyanga umb…Ē awu ay…õrhe atsen abi Uyahuda, anu id…õyiwe anera iy…õrhe, anggbaashimb…Ē ik…õi anu ikŇ© ijee adarh umb…Ē.
\v 43 B…Ēr isi √≠wengge rimi ru umbi. Ub…õn uwuku ubee ig…Ēng ru umbi awu ufang unga awu ug√£rh√£mbi.
\v 44 Ik…õi ub…õn unera aka abee iwu unggbaashi, awu ufang unga awuri iwu ug√£rh√£ ra anera kishoo.
\v 45 Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner asi ibanga umb…Ē at…ĒŐÉwe unga itser, b…Ēr unga awuri iwu ug√£rh√£, na adzowe urh…õnga af…Ērh anera arh…õrh…õ.>>
\s1 Uner itapa akpoa iny√£ anang
\r (Umat 20.29-34; Irh 18.35-43)
\p 
\v 46 Uyesu nu angw…õŐÉ imesanga aka azń© atsń© Ujeriko. Umb…Ē nu anera arh…õrh…õ, awuri idze utepa, uner itapa agburh Ubartimawu agbena agburh <<ungw…õŐÉ Utimawu,>> asei nu ubang utsń©ndń©√£ anu if…õn.
\v 47 Ivangy…õ unga aka agŇ© ug…õ Uyesu uner Unazarat unga at…Ēng, unga atsarhi irhaknga ayisa ag…õ, <<Uyesu Ungw…õŐÉ Udauda ugŇ© atorh umum!>>
\p 
\v 48 Anera ab…Ē…Ē arh…õrh…õ ats…õrha unga ag…õ, <<Unu ukutata!>> B…Ēr unga agbisha atsarhi irhaknga akarh√£rh√£ ayisa ag…õ, <<A Ungw…õŐÉ Udauda, uma ugŇ© atorh umum!>>
\p 
\v 49 Uyesu atsurha ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ na ag…õ, <<√Äka ayisuwa unga.>> Umb…Ē ayisu uner itapa ha, ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ug…Ēm! Usisok, ayisa ungo.>>
\v 50 Unga atare untamanga, na akatasok ater isha, azń©√£ ru Uyesu.
\p 
\v 51 Uyesu arhusa unga ag…õ, <<Ungo ubee umum ikorhuwa ungo use?>>
\p Uner itapa ha ag…õ, <<A Uteiya, umum ibee iny√£ anang.>>
\p 
\v 52 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Uzń©…Ē. Imangmangngo ngge ikerhuwa ungo.>> Kanying unga ay…õisa inyń©ny√£nga na ad…Ēsu Uyesu umb…Ē uzń©mb…Ē nu utsń©ndń©.
\c 11
\s1 Uyesu atsń© Urusharhima nggu ininang
\r (Umat 21.1-11; Irh 19.28-40; Uyoh 12.12-19)
\p 
\v 1 Umb…Ē aka aba akhapa ru Urusharhima ru Ubetafaji ru Ubetani IgŇ© Acucii Uzaitun, Uyesu adene angw…õŐÉ imesanga avaa.
\v 2 Ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka azń© ru ungw…õŐÉrhŇ© uteu ukp…Ē…Ē ra asumbi, ub…õn itsitsń©mbi, umbi awuri iny√£mbi ungw…õŐÉ uzhika umb…Ē aka abow, unera aka anasi ifŇ©√£ umgb…Ē. √Äka agarha umgb…Ē akŇ© aba.
\v 3 Unera aba arhusunga umbi ag…õ, <Awu use umbi akorhe rimi?> √Äka ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <Uteijee unga abeea umgb…Ē unga awuri ibvui adene umgb…Ē uba kanying.> >>
\p 
\v 4 Umb…Ē azń© any√£ ungw…õŐÉ uzhika uku ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ru ubang utsń©ndń©√£, ubow ra angwń© iya. Umb…Ē atirhi igarha umgb…Ē.
\v 5 Abirab…õ aka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ um…Ē arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu umbi agarhu ungw…õŐÉ uzhika ha?>>
\v 6 Umb…Ē adzipa arherhe ubinkpi Uyesu aka ad…õyiwe umb…Ē. Aner ha neke umb…Ē akŇ© ungw…õŐÉ uzhika ha azń©mb…Ē.
\v 7 Ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka akŇ© ungw…õŐÉ uzhika ha aba ru Uyesu na ab…õtuwe antamamb…Ē nu undzingmgb…Ē, Uyesu afŇ© asei nu umgb…Ē.
\v 8 Anera arh…õrh…õ ab…õtuwe antamamb…Ē nu utsń©ndń©√£, ab…Ē…Ē agb…õyi ayerhe ri icang ab…õtuwe nu utsń©ndń©√£.
\v 9 Abika awu ra asunga na abika aba ra andzingnga atsui ivum ag…õ,
\q1 <<Ikpikpoi iwe ru Unum!\f + \fr 11.9 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Amb 118.26\xt*\ft .\f*
\q1 Idorh iwe nggu unga aka aba ri itsok Uteijee!
\q1 
\v 10 Idorh iwe ri ibiba iy…õrhe ut…õm…õn Udauda!
\q1 Ikpikpoi iwe afaf√£ ra af√£.>>
\p 
\v 11 Uyesu aka atsń© Urusharhima, azń©√£ ri Iya-Num atsń© arhisa abina kishoo. Nggay…õ unum uku utsń©kp…Ē, nggee unga abvui adzek azń©√£ Ubetani nggu angw…õŐÉ imesanga us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn.
\s1 Uyesu atsuke ikponum ru uvorhvo
\r (Umat 21.18-19)
\p 
\v 12 Ukpe unum uvaa umb…Ē aka asoku Ubetani, imerh if…õr Uyesu.
\v 13 Unga aka any√£ ucucii uvorhvo ukukaa uku ukpusha ayerhe ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉ, unga azń©a ibee ikpŇ©rh√£ ru umgb…Ē. Ivangy…õ unga aka azń© atsń© ru umgb…Ē, unga asi ikpoa ubin, ayerhe ukpekŇ© ake akpusha ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ, ubinkutsu, asi iwea ivang ikpŇ©rhŇ© uvorhvo.
\v 14 M…Ēc…õ unga ag…Ēr uvorhvo ha ag…õ, <<Unera niba abvui aghaa ikpŇ©rh√£ngo ugbagbaa!>> Angw…õŐÉ imesa igamb…Ē agŇ©mb…Ē ubinkpi unga aka arherhe.
\s1 Uyesu asare Iya-Num
\r (Umat 21.12-17; Irh 19.45-48; Uyoh 2.13-22)
\p 
\v 15 Umb…Ē aka atsń© Urusharhima, Uyesu atsń© ri Iya-Num atirha awayiwe abika agoi igoi nu abika agugoyiwe um…Ē. Akw…õr atsime atebur abika afaruwe uhw…õk nu anang isei abika agoyiwe anurh…õu.
\v 16 Ak…õna anera ikŇ© ubin ukpuku ugoiwe at…Ēng ra angwń© Iya-Num.
\v 17 Unga amesuwe anera ag…õ, <<Its…õng Arherhu-Num isi ig…Ērngge ug…õ,
\q1 << <Awuri iyisi iyamum
\q2 iya if…õn-Num ri idŇ©a kishoo?\f + \fr 11.17 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uish 56.7\xt*\ft .\f*>
\q1 Nggay…õ umbi atsu ike iwu utai uwoyi av…õu.\f + \fr 11.17 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uiri 7.11\xt*\ft .\f*>>
\p 
\v 18 Ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num nu abika amesuwe Ikpem aka agŇ© arherhe ak…õr…õ umb…Ē abee utsń©ndń© uwuku uf…õre unga, na agŇ© iwei unga ubinkutsu anera kishoo adzeidzeu imesanga.
\p 
\v 19 Urh…õ…õ uku uwe, Uyesu nu angw…õŐÉ imesanga adzemb…Ē ru uteu ha.
\s1 Ucucii uvorhvo uwuku usherhe
\r (Umat 21.20-22)
\p 
\v 20 Ru ukpeeka, umb…Ē aka at…Ēng, umb…Ē any√£ ucucii uvorhvo ha uku ukoyi kishoo nggu anunanga.
\v 21 Ubitru ayita na ag…Ēr Uyesu ag…õ, <<A umarhem, urhi uny√£! Ucucii uvorhvo ha ungo uku utsuke ikponum h√£ uku usherhumgb…Ē!>>
\p 
\v 22 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka awe ru imangmang ru Unum!
\v 23 Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, unera aba ag…Ēr igŇ© iy…õr…õ ag…õ, <Utang itsingo ugba ru ukau ukug…Ēng,> unga aba asi icicanga ra am…õnnga nu ubinkpi unga aka arherhe, na awea ri imangmang awuri ikorhukumb…Ē unga.
\v 24 Nggee umum id…õyiwa umbi, ub…õn ubinkpi umbi aka if…õna ru if…õn-Num, aka awe ru imangmang ug…õ umbi aka akpombi ukp…Ē, ukp…Ē iwuri iwu ukpumbi.
\v 25 Ik…õi ub…õn ivangy…õ umbi aka id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ na af…õn-Num, umbi aba awembi ra av…Ēm nggu unera, √†ka atsŇ©we uner ha, nu Ut…õmbi uwu af√£ atsŇ©w√£ umbi ra arhimmbi.>>\f + \fr 11.25 \ft Abvur ak…Ē…Ē aki its…õng abok aki isha ag…Ērke ik…õi ug…õ, \fv 26 \fqa B…Ēr itsitsŇ©we iba ishingge, rimi h√£, Ut…õmbi uwu af√£ asi √≠tsŇ©wanga arhim umbi.\f*
\s1 Acucang ijee Uyesu
\r (Umat 21.23-27; Irh 20.1-8)
\p 
\v 27 Umb…Ē aka abvui atsń© Urusharhima, Uyesu atsń© az…õŐÉrh√£ ri irh…õrh Iya-Num nukpi, um…Ē ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num, nu abika amesuwe Ikpem nu anggbaashi anera aba ru unga.
\v 28 Ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ungo ukŇ© ijee iyikisong unu ikorhe if…õrh…õ iy…õr…õ ha? Ik…õi ungaa adzaa ungo ijee iyiki ikorhi if…õrha ha?>>
\p 
\v 29 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umum irhusa umbi ubina unying. √Äka adzipuwa umum, umum id…õyiwa umbi umum ikŇ© ijee ungaa ikŇ© ikorha abin h√£.
\v 30 Ub…Ētisima Uyohana udzeka af√£ use udzeka anera? √Äka ad…õyiwa umum!>>
\p 
\v 31 Umb…Ē ak…õki itsŇ©w√£ nggu ad…Ēkamb…Ē, ag…õ, <<Um…õn iba ig…Ēr ug…õ, <Udzek ra af√£,> unga awuri irhusa um…õn ag…õ, <Awu use utsu umbi ashimbi ri imangmang ru unga?>
\v 32 B…Ēr um…õn iba ig…Ēr ug…õ, <Udzek ra anera,> um…õn igŇ© iwei anera ab…õr…õ, ubinkutsu, umb…Ē anyangu Uyohana awu uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num.>>
\p 
\v 33 Nggee umb…Ē ag…Ēr Uyesu ag…õ, <<Um…õn isi ihw…õngm…õn.>>
\p Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umum igamum isi √≠d…õyiwamum umbi umum ikŇ© ijee iyikisong ikorha abin h√£.>>
\c 12
\s1 Unyaka arherhe aki abi irham imang
\r (Umat 21.33-46; Irh 20.9-19)
\p 
\v 1 Uyesu arherhe unyaka arherhe adzise umb…Ē, ag…õ, <<Utsa uw…Ē…Ē akau icang inebi, adzin uf…Ēm adzipuwe icang h√£, asim ughwee ri ifa ukpuku upayi am…õŐÉ ikpŇ©rhŇ© inebi ha, ik…õi atar akang utsurha udedetamgb…Ē uwu idz…õu. M…Ēc…õ unga atsu ab…Ē…Ē abi irham imang ri icang h√£, na azń©√£ abń© akase.
\v 2 Ivang iyiki ik…Ēng inebi ha iki iwe, unga adene ug√£rh√£nga azń© ra abi irham imang ri icang h√£, ay…õise ikpŇ©rhŇ© inebi ri icang h√£.
\v 3 B…Ēr abi irham imang h√£ adzur ug√£rh√£ h√£, akw…õr unga, na awayiwe unga nggu abok aka at√£rh√£.
\v 4 M…Ēc…õ unga adene ug√£rhŇ© uw…Ē…Ē, umb…Ē akw…õr uwu ha ni itsia, na ay…õia unga.
\v 5 Unga anang adene uw…Ē…Ē, uwu ha umb…Ē af…õrkumb…Ē unga. Unga adene ab…Ē…Ē arh…õrh…õ, abi irham imang h√£ akw…õr ab…Ē…Ē, na af…õre ab…Ē…Ē.
\p 
\v 6 <<Unga ab…Ēra unera unying unga aka idene, ungw…õŐÉnga aka abema. Unga adene unga uwu imaataka, na ag…õ, <Awuri idzowukumb…Ē ig…Ēng ru ungw…õŐÉmum.>
\p 
\v 7 <<B…Ēr abi irham imang h√£ ag…Ēr ad…Ēkamb…Ē ag…õ, <Uwuku ugha ukam icang h√£ nuwi. √Äka aba um…õn if…õre unga, nu icanga iwu iyim…õn.>
\v 8 Nggee umb…Ē adzur unga af…õre unga, na atare ukoma ru undzing uf…Ēm icang h√£.>>
\p 
\v 9 Uyesu arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Uner icang h√£ awuri ikorha aguse? Awuri iba atsń©me abi irham imang h√£ na adzowe icang h√£ ra ab…Ē…Ē.
\v 10 Umbi aka avarhumbi ri its…õng Arherhu-Num akirak…õ aka ag…Ēr ug…õ,
\q1 << <Utarhkpi abi idzin aka akp…õŐÉ,
\q2 ukp…Ē uwu utarh √£gboki idzin.
\q1 
\v 11 Uteijee ha unga akorha ak…õr…õ,
\q2 awu ubin igbigba ra asum…õn.>\f + \fr 12.11 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Amb 118.22,23\xt*\ft .\f*>>
\p 
\v 12 M…Ēc…õ umb…Ē abee udń© ukpuku udzur unga, ubinkutsu umb…Ē ahw…õngmb…Ē ug…õ arherhe unyaka arherhe ha iwu ra atsimb…Ē. B…Ēr umb…Ē agŇ© iwei anera, ngge itsu umb…Ē neke unga na azń©mb…Ē.
\s1 Arhusu ifai ikirbi abń© ru Ukaisar
\r (Umat 22.15-22; Irh 20.20-26)
\p 
\v 13 Ak…õr…õ aka amaa umb…Ē adene abi Ufarisi ab…Ē…Ē nu aner Uhiridu umb…Ē azń© adeyi Uyesu ri irh…õm arherhanga.
\v 14 Umb…Ē aba ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A umarhem, um…õn ihw…õngm…õn ungo urhiku uner. Anera kishoo awu ubina unying ru ungo, ubinkutsu am…õŐÉngo ashike nggu iwiwe uner, b…Ēr ungo umesuwe utsń©ndń© Unum ri idzidz…õrhe. Ungo uny√£ im…õŐÉngge um…õn ifase ikirbi abń© ru Ukaisar use isi im…õŐÉngge?
\v 15 Um…õn ifai use um…õn neke ififai?>>
\p B…Ēr Uyesu ahw…õnga ukpukpetamb…Ē. Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu umbi andeya umum? √Äka akŇ©w√£ ishaa imang h√£ umb…Ē iki ikŇ© afai ikirbi abń© ru umum inya.>>
\v 16 Umb…Ē aka akowe ishaa imang h√£, unga arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Uzirhzń© ukpir…õ nu itsok ik…õr…õ iwu iki ungam…Ē?>>
\p Umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Iki Ukaisar.>>
\p 
\v 17 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka adzowe Ukaisar ubin ukpunga na adzowe Unum ubin ukpu Unum.>>
\p Umb…Ē adzeidzeu akarh√£rh√£ ru unga. \fig Ishaa imang umb…Ē aki iyisa udinari|alt="Coin called Denarius" src="gt00059.tif" size="col" loc="12.17" copy="Gordon Thompson" ref="12.13-17"\fig*
\s1 Arhusa arherhe isoka akpe
\r (Umat 22.23-33; Irh 20.27-40)
\p 
\v 18 Abi Usaduki ab…Ē…Ē, abika ag…Ēr ag…õ isok ra akpe ishingge, aba ru Uyesu nggu irhirhusa.
\v 19 Ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A umarhem, Umusa ats…õnga um…õn ug…õ unera aba akpea na ab…Ēre uts…õŐÉnga ashia ra aw…õkaci, awu ufang ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē anyangu uts…õŐÉrh√£pfu ha amare aw…õkaci ru ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē.
\v 20 Ab…Ē…Ē rab…Ē ut…Ē…Ēva awu angw…õŐÉ uyi akatsak. Uwu inggbaashia apfuna, na akpe ashia ru ungw…õŐÉ.
\v 21 Uwu uvaa ik…õi apfunu uts…õŐÉrh√£pfu ha, iganga akpea, ashia ru ungw…õŐÉ. Uwu untaar rimi h√£.
\v 22 Rimi h√£ kishookamb…Ē ut…Ē…Ēva ha, asi ib…Ērukumb…Ē ungw…õŐÉ. Ri imimasha uts…õŐÉrh√£pfu ha ik…õi akpea.
\v 23 Ri isok ra akpe awuri iwu uts…õrha ungam…Ē ru umb…Ē? Ubinkutsu kishookamb…Ē ut…Ē…Ēva apfunumb…Ē unga.>>
\p 
\v 24 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi asi igbambi irhak umbi aka asi ihw…õngmbi its…õng Arherhu-Num use ijeenga?
\v 25 Ivangy…õ abika akpukpe aka isok, asi √≠pfunumb…Ē use adzowukumb…Ē ipfuna, umb…Ē awuri iwe ru nyaki √≠pfu itser-Num ra af√£.
\v 26 Ra arherhi isok ra akpe, umbi anasi ivarhumbi ak…õr…õ ha ru ubvur Umusa, ri isarhe ufum uku ugar urha? Unum aka ag…Ēr Umusa ag…õ, <Umum iwu Unum uwu Uibrahim, nu uwu Uishaku, nu ik…õi uwu Uyakubu.>\f + \fr 12.26 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Idzi 3.6\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 27 Unga asi iwea Unum uwu abika akpe, b…Ēr unga awu uwu abi urh…õ. Umbi agba irhak iki ibewe!>>
\s1 Ikpem iki ig…Ēng
\r (Umat 22.34-40; Irh 10.25-28)
\p 
\v 28 Utsa uw…Ē…Ē uwuku umesuwe Ikpem aba agŇ© umb…Ē ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ uning nggu ad…Ēka. Unga aka agŇ© ug…õ Uyesu adzowe umb…Ē irh…õm iyiki ize, unga arhusa unga ag…õ, <<Kishoo ikpem, iyikisong iwu iki ig…Ēnga?>>
\p 
\v 29 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Iki ig…Ēnga iwu ngg…õ…õ ag…õ, <√Äka agŇ© umum umbi abi Uisrairha, Uteijee Unumm…õn, awu Uteijee unying.
\v 30 Ubemu Uteijee Unumngo nggu am…õnngo kishoo, nggu urh…õngo kishoo, nu ihwihw…õngngo kishoo, nu nggu ikerngo kishoo.>\f + \fr 12.30 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Iva 6.4,5\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 31 Iyi ivaa ha ig…õ, <Ubemu und…Ēkango ru nyaka ungo uku ubemi itsingo.>\f + \fr 12.31 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Urha 19.18\xt*\ft .\f* √ćkpem iy…Ē…Ē isi inangngge iy…õr…õ ha.>>
\p 
\v 32 Uwuku umesuwe ikpem ha ag…Ēr Uyesu ag…õ, <<Ungo urhika ra arherhango uku urherhe ug…õ Unum awu unying uw…Ē…Ē ashia b…Ēr unga.
\v 33 Ubema unga nggu am…õnngo kishoo, nu ihwihw…õngngo kishoo nu ikerngo, nu ubemu ud…Ēkango ru nyaki itsingo, ananga izŇ©w√£ iyiki ikpikpń©ń© nu id…õm-Num.>>
\p 
\v 34 Uyesu aka agŇ© unga arherha arherhe itsoi, unga ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ungo uku ukhapungo nggu Iy…õrhe Unum.>> M…Ēc…õ unera asi irhusunga ubin ukp…Ē…Ē.
\s1 Arhusa arherhe ri itsi Ukiristo
\r (Umat 22.41-46; 23.1-36; Irh 20.41-47)
\p 
\v 35 Uyesu aka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ amesuwe ru uf…Ēm Iya-Num unga arhusa ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu abika amesuwe Ikpem anu ig…Ēr ag…õ Ukiristo awu ungw…õŐÉ Udauda?
\v 36 Udauda nibikanga, ri ijee Ipfu Isarsatangge unga ag…Ēr ag…õ,
\q1 << <Uteijee ag…Ēr Uteijeemum ag…õ,
\q2 usei ru ubok ughamum,
\q1 <<Uts…õku umum iki itsu anggamtsakngo
\q2 ru andaidakngo.>> >\f + \fr 12.36 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Amb 110.1\xt*\ft .\f*
\m 
\v 37 Udauda nibikanga ayisu Ukiristo ag…õ, <Uteijee.> Awuri ikorha aguse ru Uteijee awu ungw…õŐÉ ru Udauda?>>
\p Nggaa ikik…Ēng anera ikpeto ru unga nggu it…õnam…õn.
\s1 Uyesu ayare igoi abika amesuwe Ikpem
\r (Umat 23.1-36; Irh 11.37-54; 20.45-47)
\p 
\v 38 Ri imesanga, Uyesu ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<√Äka akp…Ēm am…õnmbi nggu abika amesuwe Ikpem, umb…Ē abee itsń©m atorho akag…Ēng az…õŐÉrh√£, abee anera aghwe umb…Ē ri inang iz…õ…õ,
\v 39 ik…õi umb…Ē abee anera adzise umb…Ē anang isei aka aze ra ab√£ if…õn-Num, nu anang isei aka aze ra anang irhowa.
\v 40 Umb…Ē awu abika aghawe abin ats…õŐÉrh√£pfu na avur ayamb…Ē, na adarhi ider if…õn-Num iyi igbana. IkpŇ© umb…Ē awuri itsu umb…Ē ufai akarh√£rh√£.>>
\s1 IzŇ©wŇ© uts…õŐÉrh√£pfu
\r (Irh 21.1-4)
\p 
\v 41 Uyesu asei ri if…õna ra anangk…õ umb…Ē iki itsu izŇ©w√£ ri Iya-Num, az…õrhe anera iki itsuyiwe uhw…õk ri ijara izŇ©w√£. Ab…Ē…Ē abi ubin arh…õrh…õ atsu uhw…õk urh…õrh…õ.
\v 42 M…Ēc…õ utsŇ©wŇ© uts…õŐÉrh√£pfu uw…Ē…Ē, aba atsuke ungw…õŐÉrhń© √≠shaa imang ivaa iki isi iwengge ubin.
\p 
\v 43 Uyesu ayisa angw…õŐÉ imesanga aba ru unga, ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, ubinkpi utsŇ©w√£ uts…õŐÉrh√£pfu uwur…õ aka atsu ri ijara izŇ©w√£ h√£, inangngge iyimb…Ē aka adzowe kishoo.
\v 44 Kishoo adzowe ra arh…õrha abinmb…Ē aka awe, b…Ēr unga ri itsŇ©w√£nga, unga adzowe kishoo ubinkpi unga aka awe ra ukp…Ē.>>
\c 13
\s1 Uyesu as…Ēm ikpŇ© isisipa Iya-Num
\r (Umat 24.1-35; Irh 21.5-33)
\p 
\v 1 Uyesu adzeka ri Iya-Num nukpi, unying ra angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A umarhem, urhi uny√£ nggaa atarh ak…õr…õ, nu √≠dzin iy…õr…õ!>>
\p 
\v 2 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ungo uny√£…Ē nggaa √≠dzin iy…õr…õ? Awuri isipuwe ngge kishoo. Asi √≠nekukumb…Ē utarh unying nu und…Ēkakp…Ē.>>
\p 
\v 3 Uyesu asei ni itsi IgŇ© Acucii Uzaitun iki id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ra asu Iya-Num. Ubitru, Uyaku, Uyohana nu Uandarawu arhusa unga ri iw…Ēk ag…õ,
\v 4 <<Us…Ēma um…õn, if…õrha ha ikorhu ukang? Utsara uwu uguse umb…Ē aka iny√£ ri ivangy…õ ngge iki itirhi ikorhe?>>
\p 
\v 5 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka arhi any√£, utsur unera arh…õma umbi.
\v 6 Anera arh…õrh…õ aka idzeka ri itsokmum, anu ig…Ēr ag…õ, <Umum iwu unga,> umb…Ē awuri irh…õm anera arh…õrh…õ.
\v 7 Ivangy…õ umbi aka igŇ© isarhe iwa nu ugbugbewangge, niba asoyimbi am…õnmbi. Awu ufang ak…õr…õ ha akorhe, b…Ēr imimasha ina ishingge kata.
\v 8 Abi abń© ak…Ē…Ē asok ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ igamtsak nggu abi abń© ak…Ē…Ē, iy…õrhe iso id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ igamtsak nggu iy…õrhe. Abń© awuri izizusa ri inanga irh…õirh…õ, nu ikpo imerh iwuri itsń©w√£ngge. Awu ititirhi uver imar.
\p 
\v 9 <<Awu ufang umbi adz…õu. Awuri ikŇ©na umbi azń© ra abi ijee iy…õrhe na akw…õr umbi ra ab√£ if…õn-Num. Awuri ikŇ©na umbi azń© ra asu anggbaashi nu ay…õrhe ri itsimum, ubinkutsu umbi awuri iwu idekamum ra asumb…Ē.
\v 10 Awu ufang umb…Ē aka igbaashia adzowe Isarhe Iyiki Ize ri idŇ©a kishoo kata, ri imimasha id…Ērhi iba.
\v 11 Ub…õn ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka idzur umbi akŇ© azń© ra aya ay…õrhe, √†ka niba agŇ©mbi ighong ru ubinkpi umbi aka irherhe. √Äka arherhu ub…õn ubinkpi umb…Ē aka idzaa umbi ri ivang h√£, ubinkutsu, asi √≠wea umbi irherhe ri ivang h√£, awu Ipfu Isarsatangge.
\p 
\v 12 <<Ungw…õŐÉyi awuri idzowe ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē umb…Ē af…õre, utei ik…õi awuri idzowe ungw…õŐÉnga. Aw…õkaci ik…õi awuri iwu ri igamtsak nggu ateimb…Ē uts…õku umb…Ē aka itsu umb…Ē af…õre umb…Ē.
\v 13 Anera kishoo awuri ikp…õŐÉna umbi ri itsokmum. B…Ēr uwuku ubima uts…õku imimasha awuri ikpoa ifif…Ērh.
\p 
\v 14 <<Ivangy…õ umbi aka iny√£ ubin ishń© ukpuku ukŇ© itsitsń©me ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉkp…Ē ra anangk…õ aka asi im…õŐÉke, abika awu ru Uyahudiya atń©rh√£ azń© ri √≠gŇ©, neke uner uwuku uvarhe ahw…õng.\f + \fr 13.14 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Udan 9.27; 11.31; 12.11\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 15 Uwuruwi aka awe ri itsi uvi niba acipuwanga iny√£ngu ubin ri iya.
\v 16 Uwuruwi aka awe ra arhum ik…õi niba abvui abanga iny√£ngu untamanga.
\v 17 Atorhmbi akats…õrh abika awu ra ana nu abika akp…Ēm aw…õkaci ri ivang h√£!
\v 18 √Äka af…õn-Num utsur if…õrh…õ ha ikorhungge ri idoyi.
\v 19 Ri ivang h√£ awuri ihwamb…Ē ayetnum akarh√£rh√£ akirak…õ aka anasi ikorhuke udzur ri ivangy…õ Unum aka amunu upfunga, uts…õku ic…õr…õ. Asi √≠bvui akorhumb…Ē ikpŇ© h√£ ugbagbaa.
\v 20 Uteijee aba asi ish…Ēyika inum h√£, unera unying asi √≠b…õka. B…Ēr ru ubok abirab…õ unga aka as…õng, unga ash…Ēyika inum h√£.
\v 21 Ri ivang h√£ unera aba ag…Ēra umbi ag…õ, <√Äka any√£, Ukiristo uwi!> use <√Äka any√£, nggaw…Ē!> niba awembi ri imangmang ra ake.
\v 22 Ukiristo igb…õrangwń© nu abika as…Ēm Arherhu-Num igb…õrangwń© awuri idzidzeka, awuri id…õyiwe atsar nu abin idzeu akŇ© arh…õm anera nggu abirab…õ Unum aka as…õng, umb…Ē aba ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ am…õŐÉ…õŐÉmb…Ē.
\v 23 Nggee, √†ka arhi! Umum iki id…õyiwamum abina kishoo ake ad…Ērha aba.
\p 
\v 24 <<B…Ēr ri ivang h√£, ayetnum akika aba ha aka imaa,
\q1 << <awuri itsu ishaa unum iwu uzń©.
\q2 Uf…õŐÉ ik…õi usi √≠rhangmgb…Ē.
\q1 
\v 25 √ćdz…õ…õr idzeka af√£ igbei.
\q1 Ik…õi awuri izizusa nggaa abink…õ aka awu afaf√£ ra af√£.>\f + \fr 13.25 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uish 13.10; 34.4\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 26 <<M…Ēc…õ Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner aka icipuwa ra am…õ…õ nggu nggaa ijee nu imor.
\v 27 M…Ēc…õ unga awuri idene √≠pfu itsernga nggu atsom aki irhak ayisa, na awuri ik…Ēng abirab…õ umb…Ē aka as…õng ra anggbokunga anaa, udiku ig…ĒŐÉkpee nu udiku urh…õ…õ nu un…Ēr nu uf√£, udzur ru ubandzin upfunga udiku ukp…õr…õ uzń© udiku ukp…Ēr…Ē.
\p 
\v 28 <<√Äka amesu ubin ukp…Ē…Ē ru ucucii uvorhvo. Umbi aba any√£ aboke apfum adzeka nggu ayerhe aka afa, umbi ihw…õng ug…õ isung am…õka iki iyongge.
\v 29 Rimi h√£ ik…õi umbi aba any√£mbi if…õrh…õ iy…õr…õ itirhungge, umbi ahw…õng ug…õ ivanga iki iyongge, iki ibangge ra angwń©√£.
\v 30 Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, udan ukpir…õ usi √≠t…Ēngkp…Ē uts…õku if…õrh…õ ha kishoo iki ikorhe.
\v 31 Af√£ nggu abń© awuri it…Ēngke, b…Ēr arherhamum asi √≠t…Ēngke.
\s1 Unera asi ihw…õnga unum ibiba Ukiristo
\r (Umat 24.36-44; Irh 17.26-30,34-35)
\p 
\v 32 <<Unera asi ihw…õnga unum h√£ use ivang h√£, √≠pfu itser-Num ra af√£ isi ihw…õngngge, Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner asi ihw…õnga, Ut…õ ukpekŇ© unga ahw…õng.
\v 33 √Äka arhi, √†ka agbisha adz…õu, ubinkutsu umbi asi ihw…õngmbi ivanga ngge iki ikorhe.
\v 34 Awuri iwe ru nyaku uner uz…õŐÉrh√£. Ivangy…õ unga aka isok, unga idzowe iya ra ag√£rh√£nga, ub…õn unera awea ri itsernga aka it…ĒŐÉ. M…Ēc…õ unga aka itsu uner idz…õu, unga agbisha adz…õu.
\p 
\v 35 <<Nggee √†ka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ adz…õu, ubinkutsu umbi asi ihw…õngmbi ivangy…õ uner iya ha aka ibvui aba, use ru urh…õ…õka, use ri ik…Ētsuuka, use ri ivang ik…Ē iki igb…õr ukpee, use ru unkpeeka.
\v 36 Utsur unga aba umbi asi ihw…õngmbi, unga akpo umbi awu ru urh…Ē.
\v 37 Ubinkpi umum iki id…õyiwa umbi, umum ind…õyiwe ub…õn unera, aka agbisha asei adz…õu!>>
\c 14
\s1 Anggbaashi ak…õki itsŇ©w√£ // iyiki if…õre Uyesu
\r (Umat 26.1-5; Irh 22.1-2; Uyoh 11.45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Ab…Ēr inuma ivaa umb…Ē azek Irhowa Iyiki Igar Ut…Ēng nu iyi Uborodi Ukpuku Usheru Uguga, ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num nu abika amesuwe Ikpem abee utsń©ndń©wi umb…Ē aka idzur Uyesu ri iw…Ēk af…õre unga.
\v 2 Umb…Ē anu ig…Ēr ag…õ, <<B…Ēr asi √≠wea ri ivang irhowa, utsur anera awuri isoyi am…õnmb…Ē.>>
\s1 Adzukuwe Uyesu atsei isung // ru Ubetani
\r (Umat 26.6-13; Uyoh 12.1-8)
\p 
\v 3 Uyesu awe ru Ubetani ri iya utsa uw…Ē…Ē umb…Ē iki iyisa Usiman uner ingbim, awuri igha ubingha nukpi, uts…õrh uw…Ē…Ē aba nggu ungw…õŐÉrhŇ© udzoma ut…Ēk nggu atsei isung aki imang akarh√£rh√£ aki ikŇ© unardi ayang. Unga ayar udzoma h√£ atsuke atsei ha ri itsi Uyesu.
\p 
\v 4 Ab…Ē…Ē aka awe um…Ē agŇ© av…Ēm ag…Ēr ad…Ēkamb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu umb…Ē atare atsei isung ha ib…õm rimi?
\v 5 Uda umb…Ē agoshe atsei ha atsń©ke imang itser unera iyi am…õka, umb…Ē aka idzowe atsŇ©w√£.>> Umb…Ē ats…õrhu uts…õrh ha ri ifuw.
\p 
\v 6 B…Ēr Uyesu ag…õ, <<√Äka aneke unga. Awu use utsu umbi arherha unga? Awu ubin uku uze unga aka akorhuwa umum.
\v 7 AtsŇ©w√£ awu nggu umbi ub…õn unum, umbi ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ayikukumbi umb…Ē ri ivangy…õ umbi aka abee. B…Ēr umum iwuri iwe nggu umbi ivanga ukunjiir.
\v 8 Akorhu ubinkpi ikernga iki im…õŐÉ. Adzukuwa atsei agbishi iyormum iyiki idzidzake.
\v 9 Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, kishoo anangk…õ umb…Ē aka idzowe Isarhe Iyiki Ize iy…õr…õ ru upfunga, awuri is…Ēmmb…Ē ubinkpi uts…õrh uwur…õ aka akorhe umb…Ē ayita unga.>>
\s1 Uyahuda Uiskariyoti Agha-dak Uyesu
\r (Umat 26.14-16; Irh 22.3-6)
\p 
\v 10 M…Ēc…õ Uyahuda Uiskariyoti, unying ra angw…õŐÉ imesa us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£, azń© ru ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num nu unga agha-dak Uyesu na adzowe ru umb…Ē.
\v 11 Umb…Ē aka agŇ© rimi umb…Ē ag…Ēm angg…Ēm na abemuwe unga uhw…õk. Nggee Uyahuda abee utsń©ndń©√£ unga aka idzowe unga ru ubok.
\s1 Irhowa Iyiki Igar Ut…Ēng iyi imaatak
\r (Umat 26.17-25; Irh 22.7-14,21-23; Uyoh 13.21-30)
\p 
\v 12 Ru unum ukpu inggbaashia ukpu Irhowu Uborodi Ukpuku Usheru Uguga, unum ukpuku ungw√£ni ungw…õŐÉ itsurhi iyi Irhowa Iyiki Igar Ut…Ēng, angw…õŐÉ imesu Uyesu arhusa unga ag…õ, <<Ri in…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ungo uku ubee um…õn izń© ń©gbishuwa ungo igha Irhowa Iyiki Igar Ut…Ēng?>>
\p 
\v 13 Nggee unga adene angw…õŐÉ imesanga avaa, ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka atsń© ru utepa, ngg…Ē…Ē umbi awuri igbopumbi utsak uw…Ē…Ē aka ats√£ idzuma am…õŐÉ. √Äka ad…Ēsa unga.
\v 14 Iya ik…õ unga aka itsń©, √†ka ag…Ēr uteiya ha ag…õ, <Umarhem arhusa ug…õ ub√£ atsen ungw…õŐÉkp…Ē, umum iki igha Irhowa Iyiki Igar Ut…Ēng nggu angw…õŐÉ imesamum?>
\v 15 Unga awuri id…õyiwanga nggaa ub√£ af√£ ukp…Ē…Ē umb…Ē aka atsu abin iya amaamb…Ē. √Äka igbishuwa ubingham…õn um…Ē.>>
\p 
\v 16 Angw…õŐÉ imesa ha aka asok atsń©mb…Ē ru utepa, any√£ abina awe ru nyaku Uyesu aka as…Ēme umb…Ē. Nggee umb…Ē agbishu ubingha Irhowa Iyiki Igar Ut…Ēng.
\p 
\v 17 Urh…õ…õ uku uwe, Uyesu nggu angw…õŐÉ imesanga us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£ aba ri iya ha.
\v 18 Awuri igha ubingha nukpi, Uyesu ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, unying ru umbi aka agha nggu umum awuri ighadak umum.>>
\p 
\v 19 Am…õnmb…Ē atirhuke igŇ© ighong, anu ig…Ēr unga anyinganying ag…õ, <<Asi iwea umum, use awu umum?>>
\p 
\v 20 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Unying ru umbi us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£, uwuruwi aka agha ri it…õŐÉrhń© unying nggu umum.
\v 21 Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner awuri ikpe ru nyaka umb…Ē aka ats…õng ri itsinga. B…Ēr atorh uner ha aka ighadak Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner! Ugba umb…Ē asi imarmb…Ē unga.>>
\s1 Ubingha urh…õ…õ Uteijee
\r (Umat 26.26-30; Irh 22.14-23; 1Uko 11.23-25)
\p 
\v 22 Umb…Ē aka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ igha ubingha, Uyesu anyangu uborodi, atar uw…õ…õ ru Unum, abvŇ© adzowe ra angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<√Äka ay…õi uw…õr…õ at√£i. Awu iyormum.>>
\p 
\v 23 Na anyangu ukp…õwa am…õŐÉ inebi, atar uw…õ…õ ru Unum na adzowe ru umb…Ē, kishoo ahwa ru umgb…Ē.
\p 
\v 24 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Ak…õr…õ awu adzirhmum aki ibibemuwe-Num nggu anernga, aka idze ru ubok anera arh…õrh…õ.
\v 25 Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, umum isi √≠bvui ihwamum am…õŐÉ inebi ak…õr…õ uts…õku unumkpi umum iki ihwa akika afa ak…Ē…Ē ri Iy…õrhe Unum.>>
\p 
\v 26 Umb…Ē aka amaa itsŇ©we ubom ru Unum, umb…Ē adzek azń©mb…Ē IgŇ© Acucii Uzaitun.
\s1 Ubitru awuri its…õyi Uyesu
\r (Umat 26.31-35; Irh 22.31-34; Uyoh 13.36-38)
\p 
\v 27 Uyesu ag…Ēr angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<Kishookambi awuri itń© na ab…Ēra umum ikiyikami, ru nyaki its…õng Arherhu-Num iki ig…Ēr ig…õ,
\q1 << <Umum ikw…õr uner uwuku udz…õu id…Ēi,
\q2 id…Ēsa ik…õi iwuri isitungge.>\f + \fr 14.27 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uzak 13.7\xt*\ft .\f*
\m 
\v 28 B…Ēr ivangy…õ umum iki isok ra akpe, umum inggbaashia izń© Ugarhirhi ru umbi ad…Ērha atsń© um…Ē.>>
\p 
\v 29 Ubitru ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Kishoo aba atń©na na ab…Ēramb…Ē ungo, umum isi √≠nekamum ungo.>>
\p 
\v 30 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Umum ind…õyiwa ungo idzidz…õrhe, irher…õ, ru untsua ukpir…õ, ungo uwuri its…õyingo ihw…õng umum idiki itaar ni ik…Ē id…Ērhi igb…õr ukpee idiki ivaa.>>
\p 
\v 31 B…Ēr Ubitru abvui arherhe akarh√£rh√£ ag…õ, <<Umb…Ē aba awuri if…õre umum nggu ungo, umum isi √≠ts…õyimum ihw…õng ungo.>> Kishoo angw…õŐÉ imesanga arherhe rimi h√£.
\s1 Uyesu ru Ugetsemani
\r (Umat 26.36-46; Irh 22.39-46)
\p 
\v 32 Azń©mb…Ē anangk…õ umb…Ē iki iyisa Ugetsemani, Uyesu ag…Ēr angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<√Äka asei nggimi umum izń© if…õn-Num.>>
\v 33 Unga akŇ© Ubitru, nggu Uyaku nu Uyohana. Awu um…Ē nukpi unga atirhunga igŇ© ighong akarh√£rh√£.
\v 34 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<IgŇ© ighongy…õ iki iwe ra am…õnmum id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ if…õrngge umum. √Äka asei nggimi na adz…õu.>>
\p 
\v 35 Unga aka azń© ra asu ukunjiir, na agba nu abń©, af…õn-Num ug…õ ngge iba im…õŐÉngge, umb…Ē anyanguwe ivang ayetnum ak…õr…õ ru unga.
\v 36 Unga ag…õ, <<Abba,\f + \fr 14.36 \ft Abba ri idŇ© Uaramayak igburh <<Ut…õ>>.\f* Ut…õ, ub…õn ubina im…õŐÉngge ru ungo. Unyanguwa ukp…õwa ayetnum ak…õr…õ ru umum. B…Ēr asi iwea ubinkpi umum iki ibee, b…Ēr awu ubinkpi ungo uku ubee.>>
\p 
\v 37 M…Ēc…õ unga abvui aba any√£ angw…õŐÉ imesa ha ikitatamb…Ē awu ru urh…Ē. Unga ag…Ēr Ubitru ag…õ, <<Ungo uwu ru urh…Ē? Ungo usi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ idz…õup…Ē ukara unying?
\v 38 √Äka adz…õu na af…õn-Num utsur umbi agbambi ru undeya. Idzidz…õrhe ipfu ibemungge b…Ēr iyor isi ikerngge.>>
\p 
\v 39 Abvui azń©a if…õn-Num, arherhe irh…õm iyi inggbaashia.
\v 40 M…Ēc…õ unga abvui aba ik…õi, akpo umb…Ē awu ru urh…Ē asumb…Ē awu nggu urh…Ē akarh√£rh√£. Umb…Ē ashimb…Ē nu ubinkpi umb…Ē aka is…Ēme unga.
\p 
\v 41 Ivangy…õ unga aka abvui aba ide untaar, unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi ana awu ru urh…Ē nu iwiwosha? Iki im…õŐÉ m…Ēn…Ē! Ivanga iki ibangge. Uny√£, umb…Ē aka agha-dak Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner na atsuke unga ra abok abi arhim.
\v 42 √Äka asisok um…õn izń©m…õn! Uwuku ugha adakmum uwi aka abanga!>>
\s1 Adzur Uyesu
\r (Umat 26.47-56; Irh 22.47-53; Uyoh 18.3-12)
\p 
\v 43 Uyesu awu ra arherhe nukpi, umb…Ē any√£ Uyahuda, unying ra angw…õŐÉ imesanga us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£. Unga aba nggu anera arh…õrh…õ aka akp…Ēm igbong nu akon akika ader. Ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num, abika amesuwe Ikpem nu akakŇ©mb…Ē aka adene umb…Ē.
\p 
\v 44 Uyahuda, uwuku ugha adak Uyesu, aka as…Ēmuka umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Uwuruwi umum iki ishor atamnga, awu unga nuw…Ē. Aka adzur akŇ© azń©. Aka angw…õŐÉdz…õn na adz…õu unga.>>
\v 45 Uyahuda aka aba, unga adarha azń©√£ ru Uyesu, ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A umarhem!>> na ashor atamnga.
\v 46 Anera adzur Uyesu akp…Ēm unga uku ungbongbong.
\v 47 B…Ēr unying ra aw…õ imesu Uyesu uwuku ukhapa ru unga, aw…Ē…Ēr ikon iki idernga, azharhuwe uto ug√£rhŇ© Ukug…Ēng Uwuku Udzowe Id…õm-Num.
\p 
\v 48 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi adzeka nggu igbong nu akon aka ader adzur umum ug…õ umum iwu uv…õu?
\v 49 Ub…õn unuma umum iwu nggu umbi ri Iya-Num imesuwa umbi, umbi asi idzurmbi umum. B…Ēr awu ufang its…õng Arherhu-Num itsuif…õr.>>
\v 50 M…Ēc…õ kishoo angw…õŐÉ imesa ha atń© ab…Ēre unga.
\p 
\v 51 Uw…õdz…õm nuw…Ē, atamu untama ukpekŇ© na ad…Ēsu Uyesu. Ri ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka adzur unga,
\v 52 unga aneke untamanga ra abokmb…Ē na atń© igbń©rhń©.
\s1 Uyesu nggu abi udzepurhe
\r (Umat 26.57-68; Irh 22.54-55,63-71; Uyoh 18.13-14,19-24)
\p 
\v 53 AkŇ© Uyesu azń© ru Ukug…Ēng Uwuku Udzowe Id…õm-Num, nu ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num, nu ik…õi abika amesuwe Ikpem nu akakŇ© ak…Ēng.
\v 54 Ubitru ad…Ēsa unga, b…Ēr ukukaa-ukukaa. Atsń© ru uf…Ēm iya Ukug…Ēng Uwuku Udzowe Id…õm-Num. Um…Ē unga aka asei iw…õr urha nggu adogerhi ha.
\p 
\v 55 Ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num nu kishoo abi udzepurhe abee ubinkpi uku iwe ideka ri itsi Uyesu, umb…Ē af…õre unga, b…Ēr umb…Ē asi ikpomb…Ē.
\v 56 Anera arh…õrh…õ aka adzowe ideka igb…õrangwń©, b…Ēr angwń©mb…Ē asi iweke unying.
\p 
\v 57 M…Ēc…õ ab…Ē…Ē asok ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ, adzowe ideka igb…õrangwń© ru unga ag…õ,
\v 58 <<Um…õn igŇ© unga ag…Ēr ag…õ, <Umum iwuri isipuwe Iya-Num ik…õr…õ anera aka adzin, ni idzin ik…Ē…Ē ri inuma itaar, ikirik…õ iki isi iwengge idzin unera.> >>
\v 59 Kishoo rimi h√£ idekamb…Ē isi iwengge unying.
\p 
\v 60 M…Ēc…õ Ukug…Ēng Uwuku Udzowe Id…õm-Num asok ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ra ateumb…Ē, arhusu Uyesu ag…õ, <<Ungo usi √≠dzipungo arherhe? Awu use uwe ri idekay…õ umb…Ē aka adzowe ri itsingo?>>
\v 61 B…Ēr Uyesu anukutata asi idzipuka, Ukug…Ēng Uwuku Udzowe Id…õm-Num h√£ abvui arhusa unga ag…õ, <<Awu ungo uwu Ukiristo Ungw…õŐÉ Uwu Idorh?>>
\p 
\v 62 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Awu umum. Ik…õi umbi awuri iny√£mbi Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner aka isei nu ubok ugha Uwu Ijee, ik…õi awuri iba nu am…õ…õ afaf√£ ra af√£.>>
\p 
\v 63 Ukug…Ēng Uwuku Udzowe Id…õm-Num h√£ avapuwe atorhanga, na ag…õ, <<Um…õn ibee ideka iyikisong ik…õi?
\v 64 Umbi agŇ©mbi unga aka arhenu Unum! Awu use uwu itsŇ©w√£mbi?>>
\p Anera kishoo arherhe ag…õ, <<Agbaa! Af…õre unga!>>
\v 65 M…Ēc…õ ab…Ē…Ē atirha ashau aci atsuyiwe unga, abope asunga, ik…õi akw…õre unga ugw…õ…õ, anu ig…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ud…õyiwa um…õn, ungaa akw…õr ungo!>> M…Ēc…õ adogerhi abi udzepurhe ha akŇ© unga azń©mb…Ē na akw…õr unga.
\s1 Ubitru ag…õ Uyesu asi iwea uwu unga
\r (Umat 26.69-75; Irh 22.56-62; Uyoh 18.15-18,25-27)
\p 
\v 66 Ubitru iganga awu un…Ēr uf…Ēm iya ha, unaa uw…Ē…Ē ra anang itser Ukug…Ēng Uwuku Udzowe Id…õm-Num aba.
\v 67 Unga aka any√£ Ubitru aka asei iw…õr urha, unga angw…õŐÉdz…õn na arhi unga, na ag…õ, <<Ungo uwu nggu Uyesu uner Unazarat ha!>>
\p 
\v 68 B…Ēr Ubitru ats…õyinga ag…õ, <<Umum isi ihw…õng ubinkpi ungo uku urherhe.>> Unga aka arherhe rimi amaa, unga asok atsń© ru udzepurhe iya ha. Kanying ik…Ē igb…õr ukpee.
\p 
\v 69 Unna h√£ aka abvui any√£ unga um…Ē, unga ad…õyiwe abirab…õ aka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ um…Ē ag…õ, <<Uw…õr…õ awu nggu umb…Ē.>>
\v 70 Ik…õi Ubitru abvui ats…õyinga.
\p Ivanga ukunjiir iki it…Ēng, abirab…õ aka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ akhapa ru Ubitru ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Asi iwea ubin its…õyi, ungo uwu nggu umb…Ē, ungo usi iwea uner Ugarhirhi?>>
\p 
\v 71 M…Ēc…õ Ubitru atirhunga ifuw atsukuka ikponum nu itsinga, ayirh uyirh ra asumb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umum isi ihw…õng utsakwi umbi aka anu irherhe ri itsinga.>>
\p 
\v 72 Kanying ik…Ē ibvui igb…õr ukpee ide uvaa. M…Ēc…õ Ubitru ayita arherhe Uyesu aka ad…õyiwe unga ag…õ, <<Ungo its…õyingo ihw…õng umum idiki itaar ri ik…Ē id…Ērhi igb…õr ukpee idiki ivaa.>> Ngge unga atsń©√£ iciu akpe.
\c 15
\s1 AkŇ© Uyesu azń© ru ugomna Ubirhatu
\r (Umat 27.1-2,11-14; Irh 23.1-5; Uyoh 18.28-38)
\p 
\v 1 Ri ig…ĒŐÉkpeeka ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num nu akakŇ©, nu abika amesuwe Ikpem, nu kishoo abi itser udzepurhe ak…õki itsŇ©w√£. Umb…Ē abow Uyesu akŇ©na unga azń©mb…Ē ra asu Ubirhatu.
\p 
\v 2 Ubirhatu arhusa unga ag…õ, <<Awu ungo uwu uy…õrhe abi Uyahuda?>>
\p Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ungo uku urherhungo.>>
\p 
\v 3 Ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num h√£, agb…õyi urherhe atsuke unga ra abina arh…õrh…õ.
\v 4 Ngge ik…õi Ubirhatu arhusa unga ag…õ, <<Uny√£ arh…õrha abinmb…Ē aka agb…õyi atsuka ungo. Ungo usi √≠dzipungo arherhe?>>
\p 
\v 5 B…Ēr Uyesu asi idzipunga arherhe. Ubirhatu adzeidzeu.
\s1 Atsu ufai akpe ru Uyesu
\r (Umat 27.15-26; Irh 23.13-25; Uyoh 18.39‚ÄĒ19.16)
\p 
\v 6 Ic…õ awu ugau ugomna aka isaka atsŇ©we unerwi umb…Ē aka abow ru ugborzń©, uwuruwi anera aki ibee ru unum Irhowa Iyiki Igar Ut…Ēng.
\v 7 Uw…Ē…Ē ruw…Ē itsoka igburh Ubaraba, uvau isoyam…õn nu if…õr uner itsu umb…Ē agbange unga ru ugborzń© h√£ nggu ab…Ē…Ē.
\v 8 Ikik…Ēnga iba if…õn Ubirhatu unga akorhuwe ubin unga aka abayi ikikorhe.
\p 
\v 9 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi abee umum itsŇ©w√£ Uy…õrha abi Uyahuda ru umbi?>>
\v 10 Unga ahw…õnga ag…õ awu uny…õŐÉ…õŐÉ utsu ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num atsuke Uyesu ru uboknga.
\v 11 B…Ēr ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num atsu anera ag…Ēr ag…õ aneke Uyesu ru ugborzń©, na atsŇ©we Ubaraba ru umb…Ē.
\p 
\v 12 Ubirhatu arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umum iwuri ikorhe uguse nggu uwuruwi umbi iki iyisa Uy…õrhe abi Uyahuda?>>
\p 
\v 13 Umb…Ē atsarhi irhakmb…Ē ag…õ, <<Anyapuwe unga!>>
\p 
\v 14 Ubirhatu arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu? Ash…Ēyi use arherhunga?>> Umb…Ē agbisha atsarhi irhakmb…Ē ag…õ, <<Anyapuwe unga!>>
\p 
\v 15 Ubirhatu aka abee itsu umb…Ē ag…Ēm unga, atsŇ©wŇ©ka Ubaraba. Unga aka atsu umb…Ē akw…õre ugw…õ…õ ru Uyesu amaa, unga adzowuka unga umb…Ē anyapuwe.
\s1 Abi iwa ay…õ…õi Uyesu
\r (Umat 27.27-31; Uyoh 19.2-3)
\p 
\v 16 Abi iwa akŇ© Uyesu azń© ru udzepurhe ugomna, umb…Ē iki iyisa ag…õ, <<Upiretoriyum.>> Na ak…Ēng kishoo ukpui abi iwa ha.
\v 17 Atsime atorho aka ab√£rh√£ akag…Ēng aki iy…õrhe n√ļ Uyesu, ik…õi akare ifur iy…õrhe iyi √≠did…Ēk, atsime ni itsinga.
\v 18 Umb…Ē atirhi ighwe unga ag…õ, <<Urh…õngo uder, Uy…õrha abi Uyahuda!>>
\v 19 Ik…õi anu ikŇ© igbong akw…õr unga ni itsia, atang aci atsuyiwe ru unga. Na atangarhu ag…õ umb…Ē anu idzowe unga ig…Ēng.
\v 20 Umb…Ē aka ay…õ…õia unga rimi amaa, umb…Ē atsimuwe atorho aka ab√£rh√£ akag…Ēng h√£, na atsime atorhanga. M…Ēc…õ umb…Ē akŇ©na unga adzek azń©mb…Ē inyinyapuwe.
\s1 Anyapuwe Uyesu
\r (Umat 27.32-44; Irh 23.26-43; Uyoh 19.17-27)
\p 
\v 21 Utsa uw…Ē…Ē adzeku Usayirin, itsoknga igburh Usiman ut…õmb…Ē Uarhekzanda nu Urhuf…Ē, adzek ri ibang abń© h√£ na at…Ēng ru uteu ha. Umb…Ē atsu unga inggang unga ats√£ ig√£rh√£mau ucucii Uyesu.
\v 22 AkŇ© Uyesu azń© ra anangk…õ umb…Ē iki iyisa Ugorhgota, agbena agburh, <<Anang Apfupfu Aghow Itsi.>>
\v 23 M…Ēc…õ umb…Ē adzowe unga am…õŐÉ inebi aka asarhe nggu isung, b…Ēr unga akp…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ihwihwaa.
\v 24 M…Ēc…õ umb…Ē anyapuwe unga. Umb…Ē agasha atorhanga ra ad…Ēkamb…Ē, atang is…õng ra atsimb…Ē any√£ ubinkpi ub…õn unera aka ikpo.
\p 
\v 25 Awu ra akara ut…Ē…Ērha aki ukpee umb…Ē aka inyapuwe unga.
\v 26 Umb…Ē ats…õng isarhe iyiki irhena unga ag…õ, \sc <<UY∆źRHA ABI UYAHUDA.>>\sc*
\v 27 Anyapuwe av…õu avaa nggu unga, unying nu ubok ughanga, uwu uvaa ik…õi nu ubok uferanga.\f + \fr 15.27 \ft Abvur ak…Ē…Ē aki its…õng abok aki isha ag…Ērke ik…õi ug…õ, \fv 28 \fqa Ak…õr…õ ake atsuaf…õr its…õng h√£ iki ig…Ēr ig…õ, <<Avarha unga ra abi avau.>>\f*
\p 
\v 29 Anera aka at…Ēng, arhena unga, azung atsimb…Ē ag…õ, <<ń®hń©ń©! Ungo iki isipuwe Iya-Num, nu udzine ike ik…õi ri inuma itaar,
\v 30 ucipuwa ru ig√£rh√£mau ucuciia ha uf…Ērh itsingo!>>
\p 
\v 31 Rimi h√£ ik…õi ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num nu abika amesuwe Ikpem ani iy…õ…õia unga ra ad…Ēkamb…Ē ag…õ, <<Af…Ērhuka ab…Ē…Ē, b…Ēr asi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ af…Ērha itsinga!
\v 32 Uneke Ukiristo uwur…õ, uy…õrhe abi Uisrairha, acipuwa ic…õr…õ ru ig√£rh√£mau ucuciia uwur…õ, ru um…õn iny√£ ni iwe ru imangmang!>> Av…õu ha umb…Ē aka anyapuwe nggu unga arherhu nggaa urhena atsuke unga.
\s1 Akpe Uyesu
\r (Umat 27.45-56; Irh 23.44-49; Uyoh 19.28-30)
\p 
\v 33 Ri idzingga atenuma, uzń© itsirkp…Ē abń©√£ kishoo, uts…õku akara ataar aki urh…õ…õ.
\v 34 Ra akara ataar, Uyesu atsarhi irhaknga ikerketangge ag…õ, <<Erhoi, Erhoi, urhama sabaktani?>> Agbena agburh, <<A Unummum, a Unummum, awu use utsu ungo uneka umum?>>\f + \fr 15.34 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Amb 22.1\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 35 Abika ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ukhapa um…Ē aka agŇ© rimi, umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka agŇ©, unga ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ iyisu uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uirhiya.>>
\p 
\v 36 Unying ru umb…Ē atń©, azń© abii usoso ra am…õŐÉ inebi akika agbata, avaki igbong, abera adzowe ru Uyesu ahwa. Unga ag…õ, <<√Äka adid…õŐÉ…õŐÉ! Um…õn iny√£ni use Uirhiya awuri iba acipuka unga.>>
\p 
\v 37 Uyesu atsarhi irhaknga ikerketangge, atsu ivum na akpea.
\p 
\v 38 Urhaburhe ha ukpuku uwe ru Iya-Num uvaar agb…õra avaa udzur afaf√£ uba utsń© ra abń©.
\v 39 Ivang unggbaashi abi iwa uwuku ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ra asu Uyesu aka any√£ ikpŇ© akpea, um…Ē unga ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Icicang ishingge, utsak uwur…õ awu Ungw…õŐÉ Unum!>> \fig Ututaa ukpu Iya-Num uvaar ugb…õra avaa|alt="Temple curtain tearing from top to bottom" src="gt00041.tif" size="col" loc="15.39" copy="Gordon Thompson" ref="15.38"\fig*
\p 
\v 40 Akats…õrh ab…Ē…Ē ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ukukaa na az…õrhe. Ru umb…Ē ha awu umb…Ē Umaryamu Umagadarha, nu Umaryamu uyisa Uyaku ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē Uyesu uku ucia nu Uyusuf, nu Usarhomi.
\v 41 Umb…Ē atirhi id…Ēsa unga ru Ugarhirhi anu it…ĒŐÉ itser iyike unga. Akats…õrh ab…Ē…Ē ik…õi arh…õrh…õ abika aba nggu unga azń© Urusharhima awu um…Ē.
\s1 Igwirhuwe Uyesu
\r (Umat 27.57-61; Irh 23.50-56; Uyoh 19.38-42)
\p 
\v 42 Urh…õ…õ uku uwe, umb…Ē ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉmb…Ē igbisha abin ud√£√£ awu unum ukpuku uwosha.
\v 43 Utsa uw…Ē…Ē agburh Uyusuf uner Uarimatiya, unga awu ra abi itser ru udzepurhe, awea ri itsu am…õn ibiba Iy…õrhe Unum. Aker am…õn azń© ru Ubirhatu ash…ĒŐÉrh√£ unga adzowe iyor Uyesu.
\v 44 Ubirhatu adzeidzeu unga aka agŇ© ug…õ Uyesu aka akpea. Unga ayisu unggbaashi abi iwa ha arhusa use awu idzidz…õrhe Uyesu aka akpe.
\v 45 Unga aka agŇ© ra angwń© unggbaashi abi iwa ha, m…Ēc…õ unga adzowuka ukom iyora ru Uyusuf.
\v 46 Nggee Uyusuf azń© agoi atorho, acipu iyor Uyesu, akŇ© atorha ha abow iyor ha, atsuke ngge ru udzakkpi umb…Ē aka ats…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ru utarh. Unga ag…ĒŐÉrhŇ© utarh ukp…Ē…Ē af…Ēme angwń© udzak ha.
\v 47 Umaryamu uwuku udzeku Umagadarha nu Umaryamu uyisa Uyusuf ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ az…õrhe anangk…õ umb…Ē aka angw…õŐÉwe iyor Uyesu.
\c 16
\s1 Isisok Uyesu ra akpe
\r (Umat 28.1-8; Irh 24.1-12; Uyoh 20.1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Unum ukpuku Uwosha uku ut…Ēng, Umaryamu Umagadarha nu Umaryamu uyisa Uyaku, nu ik…õi Usarhomi, agoi abin isung akirak…õ umb…Ē aka izń© adzukuwe ri iyor Uyesu.
\v 2 Ru unum ukpu inggbaashia ri inuma ut…Ē…Ēva, ru ukpeeka ri ivangy…õ ishaa unum iki idzek, umb…Ē atirhumb…Ē izń© ru udzaka.
\v 3 Umb…Ē aka awu ru utsń©ndń©, umb…Ē ag…Ēr ad…Ēkamb…Ē ag…õ, <<Ungam…Ē awuri ig…ĒŐÉrhuwe utarha ra angwń© udzaka?>>
\p 
\v 4 B…Ēr umb…Ē aka azń© atsń© um…Ē, umb…Ē abera asumb…Ē any√£ nggaa utarh ha uku ug…ĒŐÉrhŇ©kp…Ē.
\v 5 Umb…Ē aka atsń© ru udzaka, umb…Ē any√£ uw…õdz…õm aka atsim atorho aka aterha asei udiku ubok ugha, umb…Ē agŇ© iwei.
\p 
